 the food, it was just amazing! I ordered the spicy goat soup (and I love my food spicy) and I have to say, it has been the best goat I have ever had; it was an experience of flavors! We are only here for just two nights and have plans for tomorrow’s dinner but I’ll cancel and will comeback here as the menu is so expensive and everything looks great!"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0H4CUHUqDHMPTIns2RRDbhbooxoUFF5m-y912Sn4MqPo5nWKBa5ruEZmZZ3CYXkXUd0hsMfk5lYlJjd9zLPYWPgYxJPWadUHmSj3FHLEfOx1CbOVsBu0MXNI-L46MEZR0LUo9wHQo_dGs=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn07jpqeQC6i0WpnJhoNaePC7EGMqj_Qbm8hPs6n8agRHPiRFFk5X-HSHtE-MClZx9OFVOf7oFE3OjeNqERM0Pb6bnI1OEeGsJcUK4yXUqHYmimLd_TofL6Vsj6S81kelji08NirfFQ0sAK1=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2obWgaxsqvBIrsF6sYYjdNfI7yoHnmCT6tZdxTiQFUmyPYBQ2RMuvn1Aq7ZliuU_7TjF4R8c6bKPqrNzCymQtVobyDvDj8BrX9vUpArOSxRaNkqMD_CuY_4wf-rZGIf5Ctt_e-CjXlJPA=k-no""],""When"":""2025-11-22""},{""Name"":""Lakesha Wilkerson"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUsawftK7eBuWdN4fh5iapS1rdLmXtwffGmXSyIZVN59M6UyGI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""The customer service from the staff was excellent. Very friendly owners. The food was amazing and very delicious. It was good authentic African food. 10/10 recommend."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0ExpMZWtHQtwv7NH_THX02jztSC2Mmwk9ueygKmSH8Cz0m9cZzN2KeJrGQQgUdleLerFo7pv_RiaFYytbk2TaN5jaJUc3Ih9GU3TuMpSITAdp4fsox-OQjOmUdZZRESr950KvoypN5bo8=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2zsFtQB6YVSI3-PH7HhkoZMxxghtxh8eXliNvndfDMtv_edosRBKqBShyF4UhA4PWj5xyPyZFJq97xfpGXJboDGBL7FMOPrcFA9HDj1_db5WlaRgLgOvGYVR5Dfg6XngeOcxIHjLQb6_nW=k-no""],""When"":""2026-3-1""},{""Name"":""Keron Crooks"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUW8DsfoGfXTXsGxKt4_MbwTjr1RdBPRBcV1GoecLKmt2Jlpnvx2A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""The food was amazing. The owner came out and talked to us. The service was amazing. Will definitely be back."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1GUJuPazRS9Sc_CVXYEv60r8Hcgxr6vEKpDMt-0LbJK-F0VETrv8Vx1hG_T-EdHiiNpz1uBuEdR718F2uf9RitFiZXBSt3nbGjphU2bJdJyUWm2MeWtO1OhiUJzifp3k5PLX9DYF_QCTw=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Kt8mrLIwMmU39H5VgNlY355UNSgIsa2lco51_oLLteQP9Hut_dy5AZoFWIi9XhFkSPbTT7vwKdAstkZp1ahpRPkGTXFuw_SnaDpSik6gvxtTRslE1eJUuOvIP6sf7QcP-ahnZ3z03TcLE=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0K92Ox4DF4SdNFf0Idd-q-k-e_tYfPyCu6HhVyMUsgHrp9KCk6Z5paznPH-J0pQ6URAV9UUUuNZpdk7EcatfFPr8IESvpUPbEc9QPMgrPwpN391MSrhAl0rBqxP0rhQ4iU-Ukpis5rPdvw=k-no""],""When"":""2026-2-28""},{""Name"":""Indra Kemunto"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjvt6OvOjzTtKv0T9U7zj-fqI2LEPxptCmEfuyA3NX-mTGo94UAQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""I had such an amazing experience at Pleroma Cuisine! The owner went above and beyond for me. I had my wedding dinner reservation on February 13th, and everything was absolutely perfect. The food was delicious, and all of my guests loved it.\nOn top of that, I needed a last-minute dinner on the 14th, and she graciously accommodated me without hesitation. Together we made it work, and once again, everything turned out wonderfully. Her customer service is outstanding — she truly cares about her guests and it shows.\nI’m so grateful for the experience and will definitely be going back. Love this place!"",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Raphael O. Harry"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTq-V5PF6klqLNNoP61zBN6i7Bv4zY6lFVVbx2jNBGCu6LlXHKxg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""The atmosphere was atmosphering, the vibes was vibing, the pammy was palming, if I had ordered the snapper, I'm sure that it would have been snapping. This spot was worth every dime spent.\n\nI enjoyed everything that I ate and drank here. I recommend this spot to everyone that appreciates good things. My favorite bite was the spicy goat meat that I had as an appetizer.\n\nBathrooms were extra clean, staff get an extra 🌟 for customer service. I need the palm wine they serve here in my city!"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0X6Zlt3fLCht24TU8yzJyXFTYgKntmcCdmcR9Tacem9O3VYefR_SB242HxCBx4RSbZgKVqyNl4DIummT8rCYuRY3KFd1Un6bDhlUFODYthMn_KTr0jBk_5OWDmXKLjBoHVi69tc6uPy5g=k-no""],""When"":""2025-12-20""},{""Name"":""Lisa Wicks"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUR2uTYMljuJMDcH-C0VcEBnjKEAY3CuNOTpE0nGcxGQWf2Fhx5yA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""From The Beautiful Decor, Flavorful Mocktails…To The Delicious Appetizers…Pleroma Cuisine’s Amazing Chef/Owner Bianka Made Sure Our Son \u0026 His Girlfriend’s Twin Baby Girls Shower Was Magical! …🥰🫶🏽💞💝 Please Treat Yourself With Indulging At Their Restaurant…You WON’T Be Disappointed \u0026 Can Thank Me Later!😊😋😋❤️"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3BTWWHayZcWOHk1hS4sGwvqCveu0cyjS9r3dTJuTbAI08PVgdg1Gg79eSxR3pQLGbPxLcl2OfRDeeJCHbesgRtDthVHUTpNQs49P0SmD3epDcY-5bxW16rBWQzBD6e_UieAkj5haUDoYM-=k-no""],""When"":""2025-11-10""},{""Name"":""Christine"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVsb3WMykb6s1QogCKxaF8taSMgd3IG35uvKsEtOgaf5ND17NA5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100"",""Rating"":1,""Description"":""I visited the restaurant couple months ago ordering Jollof rice with fried fish, both flavors were amazing, I was totally impressed, especially it's my first time trying African food. And so recently I came back for to-go order, Whole Fried Red Snapper with Jollof Rice, with a high expectation that it'll taste as good as before, but it was such a big letdown. The jollof rice wasn't as good, in fact it didn't taste good at all, it was a bit off-taste, dominated by tomato sauce without any flavor and spiciness of habanero (which I really like from my previous experience), and clumpy. The fish was ok, but for $26 meal, the fish size shouldn't be this small (did not look like the menu photo in their website at all). Tbh, it's the worst $26 meal I've ever had. I arrived at the restaurant a little bit over one hour after their opening time but it was weird (and creepy) to find the restaurant was totally dark, no lights, nobody, as if it's not on business yet. I was standing there for a moment until the server brought my food out (from and to the darkness..). I've never been in a restaurant with this situation before. And it's not Halloween season. Anyway, I hope they can improve, but that will be my last time ordering food here."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3W2u8FSs0cvQwzhH79nXOau3Me9zMsu8fEuETkD7gudlP_X3jUYDP4sDQFzibbUV-tkHDCfQpO8Z_08kqntzfQI64QHJVS9EKXpuUz5Dnbs0vtZZnGM27Mo2ERdliNY9l0vo3uC9cfyMw=k-no""],""When"":""2025-12-19""}]",null,
