asty also ordered there chicken chipotle honey crunchwrap with yellow rice, cheese, sauteed peppers \u0026 onions along with sour cream phenomenal will be visiting back very soon to try there shrimp crunchwrap \u0026 steak bowl u can't go wrong here they have many options of protein \u0026 the safe is very friendly !!!"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn39aZDmlvZrzgxHsuPMC1sfhpgn57iMf1vk9tvsANqJrWo2f8DCRzA3qiG4mkpX7BH06BlWaak2Kpn3klQwy_ETNUxBllGJbjcKGyNQsfxfqjHtWsI-Eea0VPZ8nB3teYtwlNdSOsBVzinF=k-no""],""When"":""2025-12-11""},{""Name"":""Bernitta Johnson"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJr2USmjQt6_yauKXiUCWEnFSukylmYBf94vxJ6TK-EgfSHKBj6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""I was introduced to Guacado Mexican Grill by a great friend here in Laurel, and ever since my first visit, I’ve kept coming back. It has officially replaced other restaurants in the same fast-casual Mexican category for me.\n\nThe biggest reason? Their Crunchwrap. It truly stands out and is hard to beat. Guacado also offers a flavorful yellow rice option that adds so much more depth compared to similar spots in this category. Their salsa is fresh and delicious, and the limon sauce is AMAZING. The portions are generous, and the pricing is right in line with what you’d expect from a typical fast-casual restaurant — but the quality feels elevated.\n\nThe customer service is impeccable, coming from the leadership down. Ali, the owner, is very personable and took time to speak with me directly about his business. That level of attentiveness and connection really makes a difference.\n\nI highly recommend everyone support Guacado for both their outstanding customer service and quality food. They’re also open until 2 a.m., which has absolutely satisfied my late-night, last-minute cravings when most other places I would have chosen were already closed.\n\nGuacado is officially my go-to!"",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""PrietoGonzalez Family"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbgmv0D5YH7fyq-gNwlr0joVSNOIUgCB0DAneaIkzppg5DcM5U=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""If you’re looking for an AMAZING Mexican food with top-tier service and a great atmosphere, Guacado Mexican Restaurant at 13600 Baltimore Ave is the place to go!\n\nThe food is absolutely delicious, fresh, flavorful, and beautifully prepared. Every bite was full of authentic taste and quality ingredients. You can tell they really care about what they serve.\n\nBut what truly made our experience unforgettable was the service. Jessica, Melki, and Ada went ABOVE AND BEYOND to make us feel welcomed and taken care of. They were attentive, friendly, professional, and genuinely kind. It’s rare to experience service like that — they made the night extra special for us.\n\nThe atmosphere is vibrant, clean, and inviting — perfect for families, friends, or even a late-night bite. And the fact that they’re open until 2 AM is a huge plus! It’s so convenient when you’re running late or craving great food after hours.\n\nBecause of Jessica, Melki, and Ada, we will DEFINITELY be coming back. Highly recommend this place to anyone looking for excellent food and outstanding service!\n\n10/10 experience!"",""Images"":null,""When"":""""}]",null,
