however, it’s not exactly like an actual gumbo made in Louisiana.\n\nOn to the entrees. Unfortunately, the entrees took a very long time to come out, which was definitely a test of maintaining my composure under hunger.  So, by the time our food came out, there was added build up to try/immediately devour our dishes. For my main dish, I ordered the ribeye steak (which was cooked at a medium) with some asparagus. Similar to the fried catfish, I felt that the ribeye also needed more seasoning, however, the sauce that came with this dish added a unique flavor that made the ribeye enjoyable. The asparagus on the other hand were made to my liking.  My friend had the General Tso chicken with fried rice which was simply okay.\n\nOverall, I had an average experience here."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn21DiK6brkGDD0v101hjE-Rg4fi0EWDmATEx3ddxe2V1l5qHFI-E_BW-DxeonrNVnsIoH6QHAcs3RxBlfPBFT2IgsPldwWEMSHyPbXfDI3bQT2sEYtYAw9HoIaG_BT1_y1t_0898umy4HyQ=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0lWutBb924-Vlkua2KrBiX0XJHUCPWk9C5xPi8jeZ9V6cpQrinZMj67hQZh0_U5VBVopL338QBoKqPK2k0LhMjufifZg0yE8WgjbX3DCzbJb1d4Ziyc91qPQbI8IoRzAudyzpimhJZwMBY=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2gg9un6UJauNsmSTc5sL8oSySWoJaOy4_-GkNsCmS4ZPm6_Vm2VDJg4kFv6eJdX9ueVofs7PAfx7gLjSS03TZqv0ucz8QbGlirqQJKOg-Q4F6rn2u7YRnIP6dEFSzXvqjj-WeyjlNuWxI=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3EEJd1ctezJlqaPN2hd10jmVIljNqbXam0_5SaWfP_umv6brvtvu0gwnAlGcOhNdVoW_E72EC6Q2IH0BZtK14GMPmB16oWcKW_WggqLhnoUtWvVbrRl1DtE6G-ILBZIvTS2abGsup8E35t=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn06gD24FqCKCvt0UBLsRq39Ymn8fowJ8462i3xXtXq9pdFNqkQgQgScBaO7UU_U0d-IuolOg1kQni-dD1FU845aT3m75TZHalrc6LK_3RWnKRtzoN_yShW9Pncm-VMFWT9qtmuHBMxX3yOF=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3y6jK_7B4Qu8GalHPc6AxXcC6sSN8arggmAFiiMGShnlojkkxRHLJ2eIhBNxXatqwohZCyC8y8n4aIvFpzWmDovZHRb4UwLc6d18YPvRvshxRQ1HReUd0W6NLbiaQefvZfdPw-RP_IifVy=k-no"",""http