"ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWB4KKJi2olNmPA-j6YCH3xrPjDcIselK12cfHYblOUSCqU2Uwn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Love this place. Order a burger medium rare, get a burger medium rare. Empanadas are the best around. Everyone who works here is so NICE! Lots of events (trivia, open mic, Valentine's, etc.) and offer deals each day of the week. Great for families (even have a kids play area!), couples (lots of quiet nooks), or solo sitting at the bar (always good service and it's in it's own quiet corner). Highly recommend!!!!!"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3ZlqXRqQvJXUy2a2P2wqs6oC-yBR6fgam-KpDucTC_hQEaIEIVT-sPR5bGLP1XNEk4-Az-wUpphse6muttXhWswW_ZfANi7k0ASdUSnetRJsOKidZM5E4TQlmq2wCG1HE0R2YZ4gQBEkY=k-no""],""When"":""2026-3-4""},{""Name"":""C.Samantha McKevie Fletcher"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1l-jlQK7Ab3cE0-xf7dv9IobxCD8DUksllq-baK6-bxNOyBke=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Oh. My. Freaking. GOODNESS! Every. SINGLE. Thing is absolutely delicious! 🤤 Stopped by for breakfast while waiting for my son to get twists in his hair at the amazing Sefa Salon down the street. BEST DECISION THIS MORNING! Thought I was getting the nachos just as of quick appetizer to taste and then box up to save for later. Nope. The nachos were next level delicious! I’ve never had nachos with such flavorful, black beans and such well done queso…the guac and salsa were perfect and the chips too. And I love that they took the time to LAYER the cheese and toppings throughout rather than just add them on top like most places do and you end up with so many nachos that don’t get toppings. Does layering make every bite flavorful! My “quick taste” turned into a full on wolfing down, which is why so much was eaten before I took the picture.\nThe breakfast was delicious too. How do you make shredded hashbrowns this flavorful? Somebody is doing something right in the kitchen!! Oh and the bacon is the thick cut nicely smoked good kind. This place is a gem that many people may already know about. I got something from here probably about a year ago, but I got it to go. Sitting down for the full experience as well worth it. Highly recommend."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1hWjZEEozVpEE4S5ru0EAuQFQmZ4tmXw-hJ4xuH8zWeEZTjVgPRj8SCvbFdIbMXEOszpa-j5Ub6YKumGwoXTn4jFSQceQEBTGavhBHp2SwE3gfPGy3xJqdKc0hqe6BEt5f6dI5fVi0Qrg=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0GQLbhXShi0tfanzn85TTFsZkAiXem0qV8a7lWQMrFZWN1RteSAlZQGMc-FJaqj1XAefLLdznNpBFL8RhHetfOnfUaBN30tW9Kk5YgXU__IsCOrzeEuaM7Zs8RtqLePXrPuxCMOI0muKM=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0K4V_yoWKzfEvVWtihW7oyrNVq9diZewRQyn6OePY-DK7wsjP2huoxkKsKFNSziKKWdUhCqUIjtcachwD-LWSjy497xXW3Xx2flUdQ47wkf_kIFsx-HXT2EvCk1FdSLsU6Ku7apcgiompS=k-no""],""When"":""2025-9-27""},{""Name"":""Mehrtash Mostofi"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIbBw8_jdeyQ7q7-wakrtJVRFmUru8uCuHOuzSlRfEJhRjHmg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""You can tell that the food was made to order and they use fresh ingredients. The wings and the Philly cheesesteak were delicious. I ordered the super smash burger and it was pretty good but it was just too sweet for my liking. They have a pretty good selection for adult beverages. We tried the orange crush and it was really good but it was on the strong side, which we were good with. What I really liked about this place was the fact that they have a small playing area for the kids. It really helped with our 2,4, and 6 year old kids. We will definitely be back next time we’re in the area again."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1ReR5h8bWQWaS3zv7g4mmeSCN0hgLo6IaeKtlpqmwNTTCYBsnjjDjPBS5Bg_Wmfr4XA7e_Px4D0YcapvWDb8fdxq0tKMyKqaWX6HY11NGkPMmQh-hM4tt_QkSr797MDV46O9WyepeC32iS=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn30dwNLk4