cken nachos, backyard bbq pizza, steak \u0026 cheese, pupusas, tater tots, \u0026 bread pudding for dessert. Blueberry crush is my fav alc drink.\nAll the staff is friendly \u0026 always on it."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2raHJNCIB722RIy5-zifJCnSfUkhYtwzK_0JX32srUxSLPY2tgb2iNBVHGBPL4jHgm644AHRXwKHOtGOdZ9EBvNn2feHUWJy6A3rkdox68yxv5wM05LMUbwwC6sRVONb9Rf5Y4c6HdI6GS=k-no""],""When"":""2026-3-8""},{""Name"":""Minnie Huntsinger"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZ3c4bHa-T4Wmty25ivH09pLmcqggNZUy-RioFiIrC3uWued3L=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""We walked by this place while our car was being inspected and very happy to find a great place with great food and friendly staff."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3HpWqQnxtoWKp-7jnFB3DKUfUehg-MhNdZTx6_h7p-MF8HW7in73u45sM7ucFluP6NFMVwn8t2Rnw4gIZrUQzl2L3RjvKgTtDTimN3g8vfhhPJ9DfISk5JA9iPL14CfifyfA_eKRDVOL7n=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn28HHG2rsdnf2QzoNhF8t4sgOoL6MrosFfE3nd3IOLZYai_cf7xTI2JeQ4AbSaFcXvJo9qvUzhYV77neEFC9Fc_6JzQtHtQgbO_QlWYqfhgoc6t3XDnJm0TucC6Ql38Q1tas8f4ZQM86_k=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0nECsoRTIQL_1J0kI1JR2nPnOukx9cIvsDwf9aK-xI6ywsnQo-HwIlWUEm2TmDAKFCeY4DC4MmOSQ9RJB1oN5Ta-_pJBd44zSxdTF9fFvsBXEzr_tCn4apdqBfI3uaCZv5HyJ2sSewFu2m=k-no""],""When"":""2026-1-24""},{""Name"":""Diana D"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK2pbx4hfzRb4PvUn9T06JXXfd_wZ3HLlHQIwMqndCE6fYzBw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Hung out with a few friends here on 12/26 and had a great time. I've been here a couple times before and every time is a little different. Whether you hang out at the bar, sit at a table or cozy up around the fire pit outside playing connect 4; you are sure to enjoy yourself. Our server Al made the night seamless. He was very attentive and personable. We ordered the oysters which was delicious and the steak nachos which was good but I would say it could have a bit more of the works on top. The rave about the pizza is true, it's delicious!! Overall, Remington's is a cool spot to hang out, price point I would say it's slightly pricey."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""James Williams"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6eh46y_yZ92ZwbE8sXr_PHagMjJAANhnVBV2JtVPbSNR-FE4FyA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Food was great. We had finished a hockey game for 14 year olds and needed a place to go that was open late.  Not the ideal place for kids but they had a place in the out side covered which worked out perfect.  Everyone was supper friendly, food came out fast and everyone liked it.  They were also able to accommodate a group of 10 which is why we sat out side.  It was quieter for teen and us.  Would definitely stop by again more so a little earlier for the kids if we had them."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""CC's Fitness Hour Lets Motivate To Lose Some Weight"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVecJkXttwqudFPqfP_EhwtdHicJ80ePJP8F_Ja7wnYgd-Fkw1M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Food was bomb. Had the Brussel sprouts, sweet potato fries, and the spinach dip with bread. It was all delicious. The games were dope too. Everything from chess to connect four (jumbo), to jenga (jumbo), and corn hole. This spot was dope. Not to mention the music was on point. Better than the club. Lol"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3AOCLJE1qdrQNV1pUBC2mbHjftXrDkQyrtjCiYGvkOexGk6z-li_K2__eZ6av3pujGj_GXMuBl6J7vAH4_0ZqkmUfE-x_gFNpvNB_Aeaoz6A2qXj-8hnmG1Hn2HAzlKz-GT7HkMg=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0JKV1tMJxasIaHWAFFagO7YmBl9iKAVIuWFrHTirJ9G8j74hb4tBc5yKzQzUq6XuZRY8UOwHd_28dVkrUTcFR37Rpu4J4663hXcPYPMohCCH7bExbfh2RvKEzJZWXBVLksPHm4vg=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2zWFxdLRN8ZAtwTr