lFi1u67K_Ess0B4JOCZg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":4,""Description"":""I was at Oliver's for a birthday party. We were early arrivals so we ordered drinks and food before most arrived. Beer was ice cold and my burger was delicious. Fries were just OK. This was my first time here. I didn't know they had dart boards. I'm talking real steel tip darts. There were 4 boards in an area off the main dining room. The folks here were very friendly. I don't live close to this place, but if I did, I would definitely go back again."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Jeremy Bergolios"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6g7fxzBd9KwkLnUX2YJfTqTkdfZhPM2jBUJIXf3AFcjmRDUApAA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":4,""Description"":""Great spot. Been here a few times and the bartenders are attentive. Decent beer selection and a nice dartboard setup. Food is also good. If you're hoping to watch a game though, make sure you go on a day when it's not raining the DirecTV cuts out."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0pST8GpUT_J1jCKuHKF-WajFKE83zOKESnqi0KQc3OZTT00Oh_bzhwJ4rcNCnu9-poPGPeE23evsnca3klBoQ6qVNuOogRMk9ptsPAOEmQHYUEKShrkT8b3UG4-jN-dLQrF0t8sMYMWVT1=k-no""],""When"":""2025-7-20""},{""Name"":""Amanda Donaldson"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkt-cWQ8s2Rp8M3MIf-G5iwjVgdEGsa_Meq9R9LZH1kLmXOHUy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""This was my first time here, and I really enjoyed it. The place clearly has a bunch of regulars too. I got the shrimp scampi, which was tasty and had a very nice presentation. I was too full to try the carrot cake but hopefully I’ll go back soon and save some room!"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn38wP5xTzpB91DQKW2GLk7uJa9LTM_nf6AihP-nLk1nwaTs-ARXHUG3UwzBBNz_n_Tfd4PjbA2hkx5NvsPFl5r18u_iGiAtpmTLmI5zJJP4rvDA7s99O2CPlap_PekpQXvGEfv8=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3B_QpW-Xg2Flb-9Vl7Y9l1XN4s0s-e3HBfvjIjpeQDodHSTN8MtG6fpao5jZilhuPPG42RdxXx220x68jXtyCOTVzpVT4Vz8HWt9_1lIigR3LFY-6CS-gCafhC3xqCj2zeqXU0pw=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2SKcUachsaZnwaG-6MU6vw8JG58whJLLBFl5ZAJQbVzlqcGW4ZE9zWRNB1P3nsse7vyXUDtaiDuElEYsyT1wlSiPgBX5pIFxfdF_1ESF9e_yr1VBLtXwiPxMOzqNzAV6sPvb6a=k-no""],""When"":""2024-2-3""},{""Name"":""Trish Johnson"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX57YXJrIIqyojQq8Ylcs96vnMXg0jbRQ9toTuCC_5nrOACUFNitw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Truly delightful. I will make it a point to eat here before every Laurel Mill Playhouse show, moving forward. The grilled cheese was everything I needed it to be.....And the fried pickles were perfection. Best of all, the vibes were on point. Will be back!"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3_1AiriCQcfTAeSrRc4noR1mYob4g5aXC2GG2wWaEDbm3QLQho5OhPyBwqZgzvgipFh4DNVNsi7By_gk3DcmGJZlBiOVMxmmzs7mlNyLAMQr9WZTbsz6VR6Q-AJNBrxUHwcHkj2g=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn37KaAxbgKVbm23KIExqgtRgUXatkkqNv7JnhogeNu4QoCXq_q90qosm-FB2iua-m1Xag5BPt4r7AaXHK9rI54ev08TeR_4GHn6qfGfZWjdKPzS4KUOFYL_UQh6EDEac11Q-wHE=k-no""],""When"":""2024-5-11""},{""Name"":""Carolynn Steele-Law"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLPbo85pZOsjS7mOJTY-ZUxgPlzxp2A21Yah-tzQs0G-Q4od5-NQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":4,""Description"":""I'll start with service: It was absolutely amazing. There were two servers and both were quick, friendly, and super attentive. They came to check on us multiple times, always made sure our drinks were filled, and asked us how things were after each item. They were great.\n\nThe food was pretty average for the most part. Nothing special, but not terrible, and I felt it was reasonably priced. Typical \""cheap bar food\"". We got three apps to try (wings, tater kegs, fried mushrooms). The wings were crispy and the buffalo sauce was mild with a lot of flavor. The tater kegs were pretty good, aside from a few bites of overly chewy bacon, but the mushrooms tasted a little off and the batter was pretty burnt - we ended up only eating a couple and asked them to toss the rest. We also got cheesesteak, a burger, tater tots, and fries. The cheesesteak and burger were both pretty good - juicy, flavorful, and cooked well. The tater tots and fries were similar to standard bagged frozen fries/tots you can get at any grocery store, but didn't taste bad.\n\nOverall, it was alright. Not sure if I'd go back for the food, but the people who worked there seem really great, and I could see why people would be regulars."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3PXBao0VRU36XgbJrqNxf_zjr74r-dOVgFNavvVwvQz6b76MdJ9eofgfEaBZwvpbQTloDgPzM6sKdfrYfnAye8N3nN0B16ssVdH0D604XYwen73NNq3TStMS5TN5Pw4Qbipv8=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0ONq_vpuX0NXO_kWw8AV4oUSbagCMqTUSgNl8RoXZJQmpxfYyUy3Y2WtHtEOqiYl0SOyOdcx1mUmtxPfE6x8wUfnyudyY90R8UAFBHcZJZL-4YMYgnIKPrRZAD_Uvx_pT4ViabKw=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0iNYTpshQ5ZP5Ar5xBkb3KagMSMdHbX5KLn2l9SlWnfGx6ZBzD09r1QbBz0UHupDJth4sGebc1LulQN89BJEdf26_wyT81aJn_AuGS0ZUJAgPZepTu9sIj27e-8ssPrwaG25Kc=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2KkPrPvxnONPxz7-lgA2Dn4I_uKlSpleIDhDoka-xqGoDHT9HqK4h3AxH5pS8g6mszhee-GJ_TE1o9xZPNN6MPaGJ_oErQxOx0unRKFMCYjm1bu_0mIHqve8yJdveCMD-xWIUH=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2st78smOgjSC3rWKJ5Y__TIizAP9O9ZzORA9OICZSieAX5GPoW-Egt6kOVM-PecFwaAQMn6u8_9xm5XDUFPqBPCfH8K3S8CllFhoP5pk7NK9C1x5N6hbBx3IqCZBP2oS6kb9wx=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Kr_q6mkjdHCB3oWJb20uunCfKY3hmlZHS9VxexpwJrrm_sRlTeWvr9Y60I7Y44WHnFlilKvk5lqBfF4hUXgZzN50risTEQLY7HICdQ4QjIsZ13jaYXHngfhEB5Hzsc0F-pbKr=k-no""],""When"":""2023-10-1""},{""Name"":""Rugby"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXlOnSYH0o11UR6vgiO6SFBt8iRmCIMANKgx4ZK9-KSFUB9qds=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""been operating since the 1950\nThe location is actually a trolley station that dates back to 1908\nLenny Wohlfarth\nLegend of good foods and keep the pulse of a mom and pop place open"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3U0oGIFgBkATJ8bJuVxtB42U0QNIB7N4OLRZRzGyrtcnqcaSsLNnl_-hmGElsjgjhLrqsJAxIk8A3CE_GlzwqaOAl0ikmW2sN_1QUHnyn4JeyKxraU_3b_MHnduvnRGALLHwGV=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Dno97CBocmn8Aa2q5ZqVd8kAK1RmOQaXbG-3AcL0PqwD7K7vkhoRsm-wO2-iIA0PaLeRr0NgBKwuVTzx-En7OmJcDZlvGEOuC3RQzJ1RJQbKhbVyeXCgRvIq0Akt5YZIdtuUK5g=k-no""],""When"":""2024-9-10""},{""Name"":""Jesspaul Nibber"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUEc7Lf7K2EowrqSTr2NB6n2tar583hlcEGeyViY_HDqjGZDJbqMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Very solid local bar in Laurel. Once Commanders season starts again, I'll be sure to be back. They also have darts, though I haven't played that there just yet. Their food selection is solid. Be sure to order food early because their kitchen isn't open too late! It is, however, worth it to have top tier food here."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""}]",null,
