0RcEvsjujGZza=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3VOkwn0rlIN3H2-Z37cVPfOsSbzyadQGqyB-97GvZKURSpNRSiFQXmyNRzTcnHh9fPnPE01ShkeGu05xzwYSuZYy21Pzfi9lvilHEmxyiKkzkKbJRNlV3o5BnWcr-VHhyAxCmEeJKCR8L8=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn29tzTv9IC6w0C2X49wxcTvIKOZU_rhhDwmn1erNp9eIfK9SDggqbl1VtHI6uaMkq0mkAze8-QVZOkzoWfqdMQ05au9qbvXEApcwbwZsvGoaHHLdlFAsq4fFyopodJ9dXkT9nBt1C0aKPzq=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2QulMhr1DIS3tuLxVMDWaXcIr6hglxB0YuFASN6fd1f5gVyN_LqlM4_s8KObdREgFqdJn-Ir4byzY4MXLXn3h69kXWRSBBhkf8NDyBOsfRnzvCbOJuV2EVIXdcFLY1HIMl3QnWY4ilqRw=k-no""],""When"":""2025-11-14""},{""Name"":""Amal Adnan"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWM7EHS4w6sSZIGDY_aB6JwGAJbgYsCQ_DdBHMLj6oLnJjLqSw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""I’ve heard of this spot and I wanted to check it out!\n\nFirst of all, the color displays are just beautiful walking in!\nThis restaurant has an open space with a nice bar and tables everywhere that has grills built into them!\n\nThe whole idea is to order a variations of meats, vegetables, and seafood, grill them on the table or cook them in hot pots of soups and enjoy!\n\nYou’re actually given an iPad to pick items that you want to eat from the menu.\nThere are different variations of sauces and seasoning to your liking.\nSome meats on the menu are seasoned before they come out.\nI was impressed with how the meats, seafood and vegetables were fresh!\nYou also have a salad bar and sauces station.\n\nFYI! You could potentially order a little too much if it’s your first time, so be careful with what you’re ordering because you CANNOT take your leftovers home.\nAlso, because you are grilling and cooking remember you will smell like food when you come out.😂😂 but this is all part of the fun!😂😂\n\nThis is a fun place for the family, dates and even friends gathering!\nI would highly recommend!\n\nI wanna give a shout out to our waiter, Derek, who was extremely helpful and smiled all the time!"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0ViFVXf10tGbPG3HFVAZRm4-HOGV1Fzx1cNKg2-xJlTcTLVQBVDPavYHgWnxl3EFEwbEqlf0ixo9gsCFgfVQO4VevMVH6SnRmCmplSjfU7FduX_CGnu1dxKaspKFOWmqj8mxMGzm0Mi7I=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2oZfUfmC6BzZd_-Z9lzYb_TR0X2khpPzhhb6VWX-qShtlgITwWfNxm_ySHi_LqHn8oIqwcwtLaBqvJKoahPoqnhmJXgr4CeuaGPzl8BN1ACfv4y1km0a9oB_Rlg32hXpTw-60eR05w_eoc=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3KD3VfaGxMYFn-k6ONtf9lL9uif9gHq3GMhasQwTvQzOMvjz8jLFeyB4ZGIbce4ZkqQAwWfjBTrHT1awT3NZfF1jFb7CxV6HcpG-Ay9KmmrwpYdgk-G3M_JQRLht2jXcMrTti1wDo9KLyX=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn27FhDPzO58Y2UJ4gSUIqjz4gqJw-rBmYk7cpeEK7IF9zgkIc0l1cBRTpFG0m8FQSqmvRlXwEI9q0xez846UNShi74gIa1RN5GNsa_T-aaalVd4xlJQJi46n40xdxchGwUbVyP3g47rI4Xj=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn17nXR3ExtXK96xThvZlGaCJNvUmDs2CpM7TSDHD41XzsJHYonw29lEZyO-RNcSQnOoO-g_ttrjKNoZU3DdLg1KntJirSXWGTdW5npjqljCKXm_xvtNneDtbsPUDt49MF8XtrbFg11aG4dZ=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0VXSxp8q3GdgLi4LkkeaSNLWYIQLvWtW9tmMD4SkHg9Y0GTtzxBm2CTYZ5ZCsKZ5YpYkY4J02Y-Au7p_j7_8MZuF2GdV0y2HJdLDvRjb-Lj5fdtS0MsdnOGfHm45StPW07Hpon33EFO2pN=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn13YleC3xK-PdarecRrJAPnm5zhJ9ci28oZwLJQAGNTkrvwDewC1KJQPfeedygIwoMjwCmdzyYDacoafcCeNyuFOltaDgrpIifQzo1It0bPsGRz7w8fm4brO1PI7ocHU31mJmA2WqxAnpyM=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3DtVxhrdoQcmbr_vM14urUm5igz_pKQeTER7vZ_d82na16U34m3DK7vnhvIRNub8CHyLbIHeiLehUdzq7IOx5YSM9kbDXbO3XtZRaUlIwMbjiEZP2y4TkqYB8GWJwEJ14hHnCaBEYG6PM=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1QsdbnGBQwf6lhpJlyLwmrSSp0gDRmxYzh3Gr0980XfzlWdD29jmjGGIlVi0-G-YtDFz2K5GOYDkG_cUoQ6qZkh7t2quHeeEnVnpqIlwogsRXNfRIV2Vtr5_XpGWRRIIJhVVkOm1pMZYs=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3KMfykQqX0hanJRdcUEGxWAfX8LVgCUQ2IKZjBdQb8TlwPqskxhtYN_-CsgoMB4J-8-VTRS66Yz8qsQ