nd stayed on top of everything with smooth pre bussing. Nothing ever piled up on the table, drinks were refreshed right on time, and everything flowed effortlessly. He even brought over a custom seasoning mix and made sure our grill and table stayed clean so we could relax and enjoy ourselves. That level of care does not go unnoticed.\n\nDeAndre’s attitude was warm, upbeat, and professional. You can tell he takes pride in making sure guests have a great experience. His service made the whole visit more positive and enjoyable for everyone at the table.\n\nK-Pot is already a cool spot, but DeAndre made it even better. If you visit, definitely ask for him. We will absolutely be back."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0TGCMpRifq0f3U-wx8lGenpc1qVKyhJ94ZIo6L3xgBhn35b0NeKo1OfVaHZe2-oesYvdCyu4B4FByJWKWvoQYp0sJfPVRfn7aRrrNltLyWB1KGxUL5vNCjl4HJqRoo3R-LEakD0vTnCna1=k-no""],""When"":""2026-2-23""},{""Name"":""Samantha Cuatro"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJW6CUwTnXrdz_6DbUj_l7D9am1-J_b5Rr5-h4gl4Zofk_bPdoF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""I've been a couple of times and it's always consistent. Buffet is nice addition. Its definitely worth the money compared to other hot pot and bbq in DMV\nAll the servers are great but we especially appreciated Andrea service, she was professional and attentive and gave us great recommendations."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3jVWWJoMJTCZ7CtDJVBhaPVeM6Wbj7_FakUPX9b9VYHQbyrlNQYdWmKx59EgbrljimVi-CVK27M3eHKPE6MnpfSSpDdblpeWa3HmaPQWe-Kk96P2GaQARLqCFRez6YOHFHQ_VT_4iwa1BY=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn07pBX2hMcoHq1j8-aVBatvEGpO2FOQDaNgpr-gGyONFNhEkej0wNJlat1dh1aTO4GpLmmzgg78Pjn26l6ZOGXOE2X-0wNERo78fw64yqTc4K1gBMicZ7CIsvhmayc4MlywpjiaEy_yle3t=k-no""],""When"":""2025-11-9""}]",null,
