as like going to after party. I love the atmosphere the music was loud but that's just what it is. The curry chicken was delicious a little on the salty side. The fried goat was tasty somewhat tough to chew. I will definitely go back for a better experience."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""B O"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYyKwycJjLTGoXSftqGiSnmqZH_igt2-EqSShn7DYULeuTAA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":3,""Description"":""This place is usually a chill spot with cool vibes. However, this time the bar attendant had a weird attitude and was using different tricks to get tips. Taking so long to take my order on purpose, served my food with an attitude, etc! He definitely did not deserve an automatic gratuity!"",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Amy Alfonsi"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWibKMSkduusP7PaXXVp6TZAuhTU7Lo3KXPQRajQoVy_dDbVRKhSw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""We are from Pa. Came down to camp. We had the pleasure of stopping by on a Thursday night. It was busy but the Bartender, Kendra ( hope my spelling is correct) was on point!!!  Great atmosphere and great company ❤️. We highly recommend it for a night out at a local bar!!!"",""Images"":null,""When"":""""}]",null,
