ly be back.I’m"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn16kbuoweqT7pJTxcoz-7DigTRbojrd8HzyEsObTft9WCk7EczgIqplSVw1wpTY7U-5md6HwY8bK1b8uv7BWHlgLfHnalw5XGgjpfGJD8URvpm_N6AGdNJMonLbkGnBsG5qkue1-ZIcvTo=k-no""],""When"":""2026-3-4""},{""Name"":""Micah Gallion"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXthIRqcQmhSgmbG6jo1mWEvGtpt0CAF0aN0VodTyKVo3VICbdx=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""This is my 4th time at Ko’s Kitchen and the food and service are always so lovely and consistent. I love this place so much, it’s my favorite breakfast stop. Everything is always fresh, flavorful, and visibly made with care. You can definitely tell that the staff at Ko’s truly loves serving their customers. Highly recommend if you’re looking for a spot you can count on every time 🤍"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0faxF-UnImrj9UumNxy8h_hLAplG8hOC0eapOv789Ef3ZKE_sGEHt8qFWPz0a0xpdQdXbtNMg-lenroxuRKOxcgB__OvLK9rbhBAii6z4FUGFKiNBJJu93jKK972OO6gket0XrbW08BCw=k-no""],""When"":""2026-2-7""},{""Name"":""Aisha"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRcpSZ-gq1SFDQwMp3eU95Up6w7v0QbYmc8L5nSSmsD-TAcwOF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Oh I really like this place. I came here to pick up breakfast before work and decided to sit and stay in the dining area to enjoy my meal. The restaurant is clean and has an spacious and nicely arranged dining room area. The bathroom is super clean and also for guest. They are so nice and kind and helpful. I wanted a steak egg and cheese sandwich on a French toast and they made it happened.\n\nI highly highly recommend this spot for cozy meal for breakfast or lunch."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn14jhEJyH2zjGIbzSTqhQ4ZqaObToztW5DUuJJySkcEBjjVwt8rnBd6L0YefLv2yBs54d_-zMqEAkEKRq9htr4NoNW-ePZBx5uRFvUELVLr2aVFueLK8Jl3ACfYMsIXmhAvMF0OIQ6uJjWA=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2y