 recommend.  They were fresh, flavorful and seasoned well.  The chicken tenders were not from a package.  You can taste that food is homemade with lots of love and care.  Please support this local small business."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0ogzjaiSZFsVkYzqRrppATyAtXC2ksY7Q793UrHb9hUoAE6lqniWDDw8OWQ3TTGTKrcXlchNR6M9vBqCUPHoEDe32S3xSLqtpfN3CLJwtlL3hIJcg4m4dl6tApgMp6LCtv0Js9kGp1PbI=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn163lIc3KWumkF0SsB_hLretIVr1WbBdDg3KKDpgpNE63TCcuehOQGejIqiZjeb4p-J8BeUXA6QV_24UoRsSw9GsJgUgFYphNafVPTMPA8gViB0V6KXtYNsreGLBAhGp96BaBTRyeGvlVk=k-no""],""When"":""2025-12-13""},{""Name"":""Robbie Smith"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJK8Hl0Ev7G4rPhVhU4oj91yaXvasjB8qlNRxZIF9JADcTeg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Amazing service, and even better food. Mrs. Ko is so kind and made us some great sandwiches, omelettes, and cookies today. You MUST stop here for lunch. Good pricing too!"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3gALX882odJ01Gjb_TnCpFeccxefBwFQ9VtME9iIAe1V1D_GLuEK1tmOaF7SAT8h2ue60MDQDyM2MAzsJYopL_DenF1r_Euium8OsTYjRM_KN71m1g5L8UyRrgVwrktmMYysqAxGzNQMOp=k-no""],""When"":""2026-2-13""},{""Name"":""George Tabora"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnYietg3mNsYNxbioIo6BMzQJa-z90DqjM-CQUoQsdvJFUsiM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Was in the area and just dropped by to check it out Ko's Kitchen.  Was greeted with a friendly smile by the owner (I believe) and restaurant was nice and had plenty of tables for eating.  I was hungry so I ordered the Loco MoCo platter with a fruit smoothie.   Good flavorful dish for putting some meat on your bones!   Nice local small family business to support."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0MwSjR6w1mRp-3xbTotfN_of7nMcyaZpjTuFU9wDRGeV8ciZnzt6w24xpNVOb7oX4Krt_MGsJ3xiVRqvAOwGgzl3d3OS4NzgGryouMR2p4lEMpzr4KxNQ