m kids to chairs. Has those bathroom those acoustics that musicians love. This is no place to study or concentrate. Just my opinion.\n\nOverall I really like what I got"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1dGgP4igm6BSx-uI6sLDmz59x74SVQjxu8sJt36sjLQr2x06CxJE8C0GFl25fiyDojrbzWU-JGKeY8sKTmLIEjnnLgYWw-FFYHT_Dt3K5gLwG0IRGf9dUVrJrqWPWD8V1o__uhOSzMMwri=k-no""],""When"":""2025-12-28""},{""Name"":""Sonu John"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXi6doZzg-J7f7gNyqp9xWb_mGC9RgzflBeggwhFfWo-2slv54z=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Newly opened Hangry Joe’s!!\nStopped by on opening day and everything was fresh, fast, and flavorful. The chicken was perfectly crispy with just the right amount of heat, and the portions were solid. Staff was super friendly and kept the line moving even with the opening-day rush. The restaurant is clean, modern, and has a great vibe.\n\nDefinitely worth checking out—if this is how good they are on day one, I can’t wait to see how they grow. Highly recommend!"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn15zpo5belwLDVYJNUQ-hgVfPdYpvvFtc3pLOR6wAef1hXR0XP5GxPC7NUUAsnzvgP2472kCEiOK1LJym2TM7Hwt7hkwOug2Mjjujwo-ICE0zDlo6yf4TSVtn88NNI8moWIQY9E82BZvChC=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3ExSXbRht7EGdY1jCQI03N7y9FF7zd2rGw1uBS4J5OOBXTPQZDF4ZatvGGOd8yU_mFHJ_GculAnwxXnkfcFXnn1hyDvJfWy2wUV3QaJmHDuCbyQqUYBTDPGina64oK6I99WdQeXrjADZo=k-no""],""When"":""2025-11-15""},{""Name"":""Linda Chin"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLK7BHAlV07c41k1OjfA9fBKE1s09mCNCCxrD0LgzRyRzqycg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100"",""Rating"":1,""Description"":""Left disappointed and HANGRY!\n\nI go to Hangry Joe's in Rockville weekly and was excited when this one opened near me. The tenders were less than half the size of what I'm used to. The pickle fully covered a tender!\n\nI should've known something was up when my order came out unusually fast. Pepsi Zero and Brisk were out so I informed the staff who just nonchalantly said the machine was malfunctioning. I recommended checking the syrup as the carbonation was working but again, they didn't care. Only when I suggested exchanging for a bottled soda did I get push back in the form of \""oh we have to upcharge you\"" but I told them I was giving them options to the problem since I didn't like any of the other flavors. They said they'd look into it. Checked the sodas half way through my meal and still no go. When I left 20 mins later did the Zero work.\n\nSad this place didn't meet my expectations. I seriously left to get more food else where. Normally, I can only finish half my meal. Go to Hangry Joe's in Rockville or Columbia (see my other reviews for comparison) for a real full sized meal experience. Crimson Coward is also an option."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0bOCrc8SUvq80xXrmjcNYoQFgSvU-kVZWhfXOYg9MSW_TgtyGMNwpx2AovxQ4Kviy0jvVxZwxKmkWXVd7kTxNICKG_KcF-xcQddqAK0P5IIfp1xi1cfHGx-Xo3fvRCBPmAoOdIRyuVs8eY=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0dCrPPWaaVMNoBYKARAHRkA6R1E1ns73J0f-dwE6I7ywKXgsEcN4noqNbEAB02E6-bZaq3WEWpQHAMCjsEpRznwwII80sEEG1ZoI2EFUrpa34ZXgTK-6HpAdoSEg76PKA2_bw-986sbXDA=k-no""],""When"":""2025-11-20""},{""Name"":""Don Knieriem"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXozsAxi5DmNlcb5EgK0izuXVvVf7EQa5Is9VDPN7q_4EX9ghMd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":4,""Description"":""Today was the grand opening for this restaurant. So the interior is spotless , shiny , and new. The food is standard angry Joe's food, mostly chicken sandwiches. Plenty of seating and plenty of parking. Self-serve sodas , yay! Praises seem fairly steep, close to $10 for most any sandwich. We will go again."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1PZydx4uqcMlWApH474A_awPshUHiBN_3KHipPsaeT60C-1lwgg3zhv4_Qn5_xswxrxIth0JNsyp6Nl_3G4x_M3vl-02I4uJo3j4ApX2BBpUpmA-GyzTL4XTjP3Sk77JgwiyNOlIbEF