efore ordering again from here."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3IDWI16d00cvWj81p1YtLhk9A83BymXPYTToo93TxGjpur2_WWsY5vM7zJrtidtN0JnDli6nG-z_b-LVGIHKm_kmI2jj_fLVRyjp3aDc9cgwMRUJbjTJ4gpicbwFAuJhS3I2AlaqTEDwc=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn24QgfADZZngZ8uXrhL9mJEoAnOa5_bRCUsg9K9EWn7eeVDdtV8A03-H446YgeMXOE-fxa52W1MaB-XQ9z6Q3I6YddKFVVJCQBHD3sB5sBVSjn9GklfJyT0SlSbjPVGxlzakjWBzzAELFss=k-no""],""When"":""2025-9-15""},{""Name"":""Precious Johnson"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX0_UwodMdv_oBGbLMOKQif9hqbO3ZCY_Lh9nbSF-Zo4_ArfVxuGQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":4,""Description"":""I didn't order my own food, but I tasted someone else's quesadillas. They were good. When I got there they were about to close so I'll have to go back to enjoy more of the atmosphere."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""LaTanya Cannon"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUpTskRGQpZkY4W2lp4wd0i97Lqe337OJV4JQQRL7fUl1xHT0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":1,""Description"":""Worst Mexican I've ever tasted. Even the Pico de gallo was the worst I've ever tasted. How can you mess up Pico?!?! Beef Quesadilla were ok, but tastes the same as everything else, like it came off a truck. Both enchilada meals looked exactly the same, same topper on both; boring and no flavor. It doesn't say that with either Enchiladas it comes with rice \u0026 beans, so I ordered both on the side and was a complete waste of money. The Beans were so watered down and had no flavor as well. Just water n beans. Would 100% not recommend this establishment or this food to anyone. Save your money and find something better. I can't wait for Chi-Chis to come back in MD. Atleast I'll have some good \""mexican\""."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2E8jlj9oe-kDFjNUZxUU1Q60SyJwaQm78C4izampiW0Zqz8kPx6VEduDoKNIyARxYLC73lngsym_1Xi-9LoCDmWl2CRIEQYPguWYslsP3CwE_IgEPLPNfqZF61qGwtY4