e a bit high, but probably normal for Maryland. Selection is good and they do have seasonal sides like cheesy potatoes, sweet potatoe casserole, etc depending on the season. Overall good experience."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Jeffrey Gaona (Realty With Jeff)"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwAskL_xI93kBqxcyJHD9adqnct7GPLxkrN66CxGd7UgUNMTMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Boy oh boy do I loveeeeee BBQ!!! If these prices were any lower, I’d honestly be here every other day but it’s one of the few places that earn their price tags. Deliciously well cooked meats with some mouth watering sides 👌. I’ve eaten here probably about a dozen times. Super friendly staff every time I come and the food is always phenomenal. 10/10 would recommend"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0LK-nn8OfUcbE1AzoZc7gkeO7ZgmvH7p--ZRPRh8t7gjGqcO0WTyW8cQ4oK-4aciZqinYv7z3BAk1q48iNnccOOF7GYRyKV-53mG70gy_Xfu69rodaP1qamjwHNe1_AdEFOlBhoneqEWfY=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2dUkQvDSkyYnMXRaYbFTz1UU98jMzvkjgD5xsMDOIQKm93f94zWOffMoK30PnfpKDBf4P5sLF4CuvxPqnlXsQdgiapt-vcJfvWDojFLV45qiYLwdU3WsZEk2CKQ-pNi2cLlF64RHaS67rY=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2GsNfCwmNqUlqUOaTtDeFWNtCyvtk2V5hXzuoH6I2hiV1vbgaUi6OU4DwCnPYIfY_YBw7mB1JKz62oHdZy0rPeCfCK23F_NmpywBz7IMlFuGRDdffe5LgeNVqTc8DEYpXOlKJzz6VhSPeD=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn10uW3j7AumZFFdM7TmF41BuDtOuhfGWf57a6iOc4Wki4r8HpsLRbgGZbvPJWjvtoRbw-s5RDFvUBvepoYRfeT9GuZT5-3YABR84ljMuxI2b5t2pY4tZS6OVcsYv_Lh8_W-1T4cbkUCHtYF=k-no""],""When"":""2025-7-8""},{""Name"":""Natheena95"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxgCV2JySvmDLg5PDLQ0pplaJ4RPcgpcM4gVYZ9kS67kTjUoLmbQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""A MUST GO!!! THE BEST CUSTOMER SERVICE I HAVE EVER HAD!!! This was my first time checking our Mission BBQ, from one visit I am now a loyal customer. Upon arriving I was welcomed by the entire staff. While placing my order I felt so bad because I was taking so long to look over the menu. Everything looked delicious! The cashier was so patient and kind. After placing my order, apologizing for being so indecisive, and explaining it was my first visit, I was given a complimentary drink for being a first time customer! Such a small but kind gesture. After the kitchen staff heard it was my first time they were so kind in explaining to me the different sauces and giving advice on which sauce paired the best with items on the menu. This was all done on their own accord voluntarily. I ended my visit with a warm farewell from staff. I'm already planning to visit again tomorrow! In addition to the EXCELLENT customer service the half chicken was phenomenal! Plenty of chicken, I actually have enough chicken leftover to make another meal! (Chicken tacos). I tried the Mac \u0026 Cheese and it's a 7/10. For reference Chick-fil-A's is a 10/10 for me. It needed more cheese sauce, especially since they use bread crumbs. The sweet \u0026 spicy BBQ sauce they have is lovely! Once again the customer service I received was enough to make me add this to my regular dining out rotation. The food being great BBQ was a happy added bonus."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2GyerB7859gu84d8wXEa5EGQ4xmrl_tVIH-wTVD8cUCTAqpYzEsnJqbp09Ntz4YEjtEVNQuiIvP9Cmar3wymdDpGIXAiFYMX-1PsXv3vD5VqY09qS5tr_TzckjRsTloGNqXGXd3A=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2DEr6GGyZObQx-FURh7mIVaXtAU2xI7HWsLXqALUoa-QX8BqJ0Ib1lKb6GWYHhEYxNreC1VD1_cOBcrwcJ82V_hqk-Oi1W-L9vJ4mwTF2tuNUndlWcabYwH8HNnSD26Q3DNPs=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0R_64HpSgnjpXJSIXd_simWGXFPg-Z-dsqrRp6s3FzTSqML8p3pJhgeyuv6IN5tTefGb816uY00xDZhLIz--sFy9cupXFurNw4Bjoyd9Ft7jj-FZDGUyxVdqkIvM8OV9E3dXeFCg=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn148L8vZ9zHZ4c87AYEmYaesryzWKll-O-Wsvs_Spn6KMsBxIoHtHv8mAQShmB2