ption"":""From the moment they set the chips and salsa down I knew this would be a good place to eat. Then when I asked for a hotter sauce, what they brought me was over the top. If you like spicy make sure you ask for it.\n\nWe started with the bean and cheese pupusa and chicken tamales 🫔 both of those I highly recommend as a starter.\n\nWe then ordered the lunch special chimichanga I had beef my wife had chicken both were excellent. The flour tortilla was done to just right crispness for me  it was not dried out or hard like I’ve had at some restaurants. It also came with rice and bean.\n\nThe portions were to big that we took food home and unfortunately we were to full to have fried ice cream. Which gives us an excuse to come back.\n\nThis place had what I look for\ngood food, good service and a good price. Will definitely be going back next time I’m in town."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1pGkihtVIVbWBUJbItIwJMwhT5puqA6jEKW-kLd7x5HQ_HubNEmZP08PjBh-XSdUH2Y_h8b6lM68bMIqOO42dp32TLEGNwkoNcvuAP6mbp7xiQoeA3N28Kmomh74HbIkAbWjT3=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0iJPdAKAx_YO5K5dhiuEHcGTEH44KIqv_luneHimLeGWCclJg-vrWJJfMZOwZNP2gqM6UwiySDeSoVq2nMQi4--NsBAIrMkP21PCwL_PJhlZG3QNFF0vVeTkKCTXkLclM3G5bF=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Y6vDW-LXWfk5I5ZICxmvDU1f5Q26ascCMBvtyAklGHRaOomRcWO3V3DNGXN1JvQavsekvprsb3PPobB0GZurp5ncyyFB1iYrZF6DFae-vKUHZt6e6w9yhC9RWcCjwhrz984gm=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3oDEXa-7VrZH6QJfGPl9tixSI-Mgo5tEpL0ByGf_x77N7cMjbk9aKo4jZxzDALYkesB8grdxFXrvovi2-pJzbODbMlBrDeoHiPg9tGJMM6e5tQIna2wZLNKslY8DcMl77wXEm0Tw=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1V7ZhrPIMf0RFBJWQrvWtWNeqOWnwJqcnYmOkocHQph0_dW9mSYrn88bP7eeX2X8JYMoupiyarqNuIoUmR4t4LRV_aiiucRYFswLTUUKpOBQOI_398kJJ2VyuHXY9MTPE97LQU=k-no""],""When"":""2023-10-28""},{""Name"":""Chellis Garcia"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXuimy0q3N3u-FEefHmc-O0Sf