DRINKS, AMBIANCE \u0026 VIBES!\nI had the most incredible experience at Catherine’s Restaurant! I’d heard so many AMAZING things about the delectable dishes, but nothing could have prepared me for just how PHENOMENAL  it truly was. From the moment I walked in, I was transported by the warm, welcoming Caribbean atmosphere, vibrant, lively, and full of positive energy!\nThe food was ABSOLUTELY unforgettable! Every bite was bursting with bold, authentic island flavor (Jerk Bruschetta, Tropical Fruit Plate, Caesar Salad, Catherine's Herb-Crusted Lamb Chops, Oxtail Lasagna, Oxtail, Sweet Plantains, Rice And Peas). The tropical drinks (Catherine's Punch \u0026 Sorrel) were perfectly crafted, refreshing, colorful, and dangerously good! The live reggae music set the tone for the entire night, creating an electric vibe you simply can’t find anywhere else in the DMV.\nI was happy we made reservations via “Open Table” prior to dining because the restaurant was PACKED, but we didn’t have to wait to be seated. Our waitress was knowledgeable, responsive, kind and full of smiles! Even the owner personally greeted each table with a smile and kind words!\nIf you’re looking for great food, fantastic drinks, and an atmosphere that feels like a mini island getaway, Catherine’s is definitely the place to be! I’m already planning my next visit, and bringing friends and family along!"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1xaj8sPkF8s_7wGx6-01bcpXTZ4CarppXkurlJEhUDNwgV2Ho0hwzo00dKKsf9NvPof_iQWmUTIEhOPrzZlcHVRy3tYG4NKoCY6KKiF-pKHbAxwvtmG3ChAes2ZeQ_RTBDy__KM3ZWh20=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3F5qVpTMfd8EMcjylAbG6dVMXFoYFY1-pkxT6i5xS-9WIxMCApWlebdR0yszkljzGOFgn_PLI8Vu6MksmO5MTghYZlMVbNtDhBFfRm9ST8zu8ANHk_rV8dFE1IUy0HGsmeVeBGSeWYOc5h=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3oy0pV7yhPTK9aaO4UC3egvZwq54yweY6hI11jM-fwdr-nOCSYVR6XFzOmGGWgAgQUZ-XB5kD33mUnwqWCPmFrstdKMZIz8j_oHbBN4GTlzZSIcnoWHFrIyupx92606Osvd62wYLlIU6h-=k-no"",