nks with opening a new-restaurant. This spot has great promise they just need to tighten up the experience."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3fmmhUZ0AMBzJAiE8yTKRem77tBfx8xjEGqiEX7XvnBkLTeb-t6EYe1zOUti3-dGM0REhdhjFJpkhUFCPhBTsuTL-S_vj0OeR2J3VTMGEaXGTBDbJZByq5HoiGUjlscnwx_TOMT1eJKfxE=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3FxSZoc32gDRgeLkgo4pl4XTQHONQjwlZYTRnE8SXmnRwCMEgp-4WkkAtYWmsIwX5n60D4VysNzPJ9tHKK3JVaGEA1oNdH4RFsVLU10C7n1O20u_Kn0nHMc3HE2uzss2iGk-Fa9UV5JUI=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3u6QxVPcYH6JfOuTZORS_29llf6PPNCGZ-9tIN-mLAvPt_AEYZqR8TURIBCeidpIIw8yVPH3W2W1cDE-Srv_EDOOYRs-BwalfEpsT331l9Ob9YaJ5R2YGSHA4fqg9AtwB6KgG2Bm4jP5EX=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0VIonY_KHIJrwRk8_9Fhd-4Gf6P519-XIu1azswwLLrzxLC-w-LR0gtWwN0aYbYJiHzaAXFyQGRkJ_LBxZadMYULfrXY9a_LER7Gm64t8n5v0OPMIcm4gWjNkD4oyFvuJ97T9OUc55SzN3=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2n4YmreKTmZH04-DEB1wUBijNB7E3nLu99ienUw_v5fyotZF5F2WLx1Fg-BH7KMcQbY2vbTyPaf9wDcSkcVZmaGpze4hW0NuBQTpdv_0bBDouKIhVoqDRgMjDXgskp-W4Hu8j-a2dROz0=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3C10IAYr45xhEq7f9y5-1RjbCKXa7CAllCK5CzqyMjTr-lYb6KNFRqUMPjxFUvVlpYcSV5vVDsVjBmb__aczY4aWRf89M51OWdnFqcl-ahBW2U4BsaMz8LpJc1dtXFrJjTkPUPl_wXDOMV=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn15JgpQs6QMFpHFV33aH7Et-fMcPsIxAqUYWmnkAQn8rPc0iCfJW51JcdTFhKY3rXP1l8bWrne1EKuE19Mt7NWHLGO_8CBQXz7Q6VXNn7cEZI30WpDKvGPIUU-zWEJ2bbSM4t57zsXUa34=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2VDDSoR8kLdwsJYDyfTAQTHWnw3EizqqFhYMfp-b29KoqdhdiPP_dDm6l9gPeeOkiH0xCqAY__paoco3N1V70lZvlnURd4WdRzrHhiPRvltCYaL5fQf-0Pns1HMt48lBrAMZHc_oDZ9O8=k-no""],""When"":""2025-11-21""},{""Name"":""Mike Zarrelli"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbPGVnVui81rfnGCQ--WTL6DsPibHkXb19_yyZghfZH0COpkLP=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""My wife and I had our Friday date night at Catherine's this week. We were excited to try a newer restaurant in town and were not disappointed. The ambiance is on point, with a live reggae band playing and a beautiful atmosphere. This was backed up with delicious food. We got the lamb chops and ox tail lasagna - both dishes were delicious. Our server was very nice and did a great job. You can tell they are still working out the kinks of being a new restaurant with the workers still learning the table numbers and menu, etc. but they were all very kind and up front about still learning the ropes. Definitely worth giving Catherine's a try!!!"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0a7PMcub1gBLRDqGgcT8dZMcKvggfi9LFSkY9mRLRgock0Sov6MULRsKiRSnSA5r5lSZUyhqOT3RGWoACgIeGwCRb0M-1jDvvO1vyH9gFp8KQdp9KznhLgli3ntgGe66Zje4rKolcUNsQ=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0dT03l-fuEf7_OHCCoflTakMM8akKHhtp0fa2sUX-TocnlTyS6AgqNdlAMkj2WACELMfSz99RWPKZHzJT2MsTbdQzW-z-GnjCJoOZ4WdaA5FeeEDu3sDX5ZFe8s2DXonIPQo-_y1d_0Bg=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1p4BF2aMjKNYKO-fII4i0AxyhigESVzu-p2aJV1BDJ6UtjbN8dQwPvQaoJoCUM6LmY5Id5dnXjrFm5QNavlmtMEbB8bh3G6-GZiEm_A0YjklThXlibuhm6wXkd37uVWxY0jBfNcM1xPOsL=k-no""],""When"":""2025-11-22""},{""Name"":""Revus Deonauth"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVjdKeANsEkEZ-DU-tTPF6elnfOp2-5vu5rENzM6t03eiFILMt=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":4,""Description"":""Catherine’s Restaurant in Laurel, MD (20707) has a lively, upbeat vibe that makes it a great spot for a fun night out. The staff was incredibly friendly and attentive, which really added to the overall experience.\n\nThe food was good overall the steamed mussels were definitely the highlight for me. They were flavorful, perfectly cooked, and served with a delicious buttery broth that paired perfectly with the toasted bread. The jerk chicken was decent, but a bit dry for my taste.\n\nThe cocktails were absolutely delicious and well-crafted. While it’s a little 