rue},{""name"":""Upscale"",""enabled"":true}]},{""id"":""crowd"",""name"":""Crowd"",""options"":[{""name"":""Groups"",""enabled"":true},{""name"":""Tourists"",""enabled"":true}]},{""id"":""planning"",""name"":""Planning"",""options"":[{""name"":""Reservations required"",""enabled"":true},{""name"":""Accepts reservations"",""enabled"":true}]},{""id"":""payments"",""name"":""Payments"",""options"":[{""name"":""Credit cards"",""enabled"":true},{""name"":""Debit cards"",""enabled"":true},{""name"":""NFC mobile payments"",""enabled"":true}]},{""id"":""children"",""name"":""Children"",""options"":[{""name"":""Good for kids"",""enabled"":true},{""name"":""Has changing table(s)"",""enabled"":true},{""name"":""High chairs"",""enabled"":true},{""name"":""Kids' menu"",""enabled"":true}]},{""id"":""parking"",""name"":""Parking"",""options"":[{""name"":""Free parking lot"",""enabled"":true},{""name"":""Free street parking"",""enabled"":true},{""name"":""On-site parking"",""enabled"":true},{""name"":""Parking"",""enabled"":false},{""name"":""Valet parking"",""enabled"":true}]},{""id"":""pets"",""name"":""Pets"",""options"":[{""name"":""Dogs allowed outside"",""enabled"":true}]}]","[{""Name"":""Rafiatu Kavita Osman-Durojaiye"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbVN4zQT2Xp36MJ1eBxfrwUTZff0uCrEYLrlajC3Mhk5enHyFpKw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100"",""Rating"":3,""Description"":""I recently spent an evening with my girlfriends at Skyvibe Restaurant and Lounge, and it was truly a mixed experience.\n\nFirst, the place is absolutely beautiful, clean  and well maintained.  The decor, ambiance, and overall aesthetic are pretty and give the impression of a high-end, vibrant dining experience. However, the vibe and appearance unfortunately did not match the level of service we received.\n\nAfter being seated, it took over 45 minutes for a waitress to finally come to our table and take our orders. We gave our drink orders and food orders since we didn't want to waste anymore time. Our waitress informed us that she was boththe only waitress and bartender  so the drinks will take some time as she was also taking our orders. There were probably about 4 other tables besides ours, so we assumed that wouldn't be long 😔. That said, there were other staff members present and walking around,looking busy but their roles were unclear, and no one stepped in to assist with orders. At the end of the night, We never received our drink orders at all. This was due to the fact that there was only one person (our waitress) taking ALL the orders and was also the bartender , expected to make the drinks (SMH) .\n\nThe food itself was good and actually arrived sooner than we anticipated.  The flavors were good, and the dishes we did receive were well-prepared. However, some of our orders were served incomplete, which added to the frustration. SMH\n\nOverall, while the food and the beautiful decor show that Skyvibe has great potential, the service and coordination need significant improvement. The experience didn’t quite live up to the upscale vibe the restaurant presents. If you value your money and want to experience good authentic African food with great vibe...this is NOT it .I ll not be going back to this place 😒"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2aa2_SN47IGaLbhemLLDHTMrOibCAB4C0yujLWPa6L-v8AnM976BACZNg-jEfMGDo_a7sMZpWPJehT678r9kTuSdeCxECerh0NxGyz38YvzIzAPXWJpibHkZgxmXIB1rm4RHn3AqPxSsY=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3S0cBpQ9M2jugJpCIa4jAPFn80aeQmHFG_50b_j74nQ-LCfjpxMc2xbS-OOnYOe-6kzsgzQ9hddDtesEgejfE_zx7nWShvnl9qF57bWpnoc786c1agCJVjM6V33R6v1QkBLkY1fCJRHKQ=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2u6aoU3UCyRQVdMd2I0ZdlY8f4zQjrPUZqlReZ_5o45u0xQ_LDw5tHwL1loq3jIziaThdq4Uvfsia6a_9OMrItTxfCOnZhpccIZqMi4ZejO-zpKl7EW1hY6Dq0xYFaXBZ2UMt7MHJwyf4w=k-no""],""When"":""2026-3-3""},{""Name"":""Amal Adnan"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWM7EHS4w6sSZIGDY_aB6JwGA