UHro1viMRQkUU1hlb9Y9xGFm6ApfcCPSQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":1,""Description"":""Ordered two orders of double walnut shrimp with fried rice.  As I don’t live anywhere near this store, it was not in my best interest to return back and dispute in-person.  Had one of the two orders for lunch.  Had half of the second order for dinner.  Somehow, the meal was not satisfying as I was accustomed to at a different location.  Rice had lumps, shrimp was cold and did not taste fresh from the stove. It did appear that big rice and shrimp may have been leftovers from previous day and as such me being an early morning customer was its recipient.  I did feel the after effects the following morning.  I spent considerable time sitting on the throne in the bathroom.  Perhaps, I should have come in the middle of the day ensuring that the dish would be fresh off the stove.  Food poisoning!  Needless to say, i may not be returning back to this location."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2FG9evc3fD2S0mjieZP_bE5tLqa_7IOZZkiivYC4zNQVEDQqykCBUgAbCd4He26vlv-nYepNoRciq4flJVJQpgW31iddm_Ldr_xJ8UKNf54yynWBIQg5ORTXKqIIFVWuTproIV=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn19SjbheDt4uwx3bFshl3AMjR0aGhFvtM1BL6Juv2tBYFoG7VCdJJKoNhONSwVJx-5A0KUcwqbYbC-i6sLBawFryQNnKqjngF9gSciKhs0WrVG75du4uBtmGUTZ3g3NimJdobuupg=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1hAEWM2-3p7yV5J0CjgeYoCUej7dSYI7Df1cSk5hVEHH2IkrLhPfvdZWXDC1OT3yEcFREZbs2rUzoJqAXot3fVUsVt-KV7aSqocHJYBjS_3HVm5nzXF6Ye7P950n-NBX10Qxf4=k-no""],""When"":""2025-1-2""},{""Name"":""Jennifer Hernandez"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJW-uWzdXcozBgtpgHfuToik6_7Rt0R0fdV88GbkbuSKTtwYg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":1,""Description"":""The people who work here provide terrible service to those of us who come to pick up Uber and DoorDash orders. They don't like serving us, and we have to leave without our orders because the employees won't serve drivers. I think tha