VACLP6tFHU4cGooo1bBA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""This location has always provided fresh food and great customer service. But today, February 15, 2026 was exceptionally a great experience at this location. I accidentally left my wallet an by the grace of God when I returned to the store the cashier had my wallet,  prior to me leaving the wallet the food that I purchased definitely met my expectations and the customer service that was provided to me by Fanta was extremely welcoming and a true display of great customer service. The entire from line interacted with me as I had multiple orders. I definitely give this location a 10/10 on multiple occasions"",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Michele A."",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdjf_stYwMG5truy-ZLHVMZz2qqqu3hGHCUzJ_6Y3y9oMOeAL1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100"",""Rating"":2,""Description"":""Usually this location provides quality food, but tonight, the chicken was burned and very dry. Did they fry the chicken in old oil? Plus, the customer service was not stellar. The owner should provide the employees management and customer service training. Or, his business will not prosper!! Greatly disappointed!"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn12x0w6Zu5B8lPIQAVU3oL3v3vWYLgrUk7wYZM-Tw48aaC3nTCKACoRi43dIFHERhcMUGqDQFMykrFUMiyWCTVct7-mgrhihVuyIzVzPkqHVM1zmrkIMlh4sYgj5i4l6jImH2nu0fWCZkuP=k-no""],""When"":""2025-8-5""},{""Name"":""IP Address"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTvRugC3Sm1-0jsdTBaCzjq2eEwoj6a-Q3stg1-5-TvDEfdv4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":1,""Description"":""Been going to this location for years and it's a mixed bag but overall sad. The food's good when it's made correctly, great flavor and texture. Never dealt with an angry jerk employee here either.\n\nThe downsides are that the quality can be inconsistent and they frequently get orders wrong. I've gotten tenders that taste amazing and other times literally have the texture of pencil erasers. The past few times I've gone they've given me the wrong chicken every single time. Don't bother ordering spicy here because they're going to give you regular, and if you're in the drive through there's no easy way to tell other than having to bite into it to make sure it's correct. That's ridiculous, I shouldn't have to shove food into my mouth while driving just to make sure they didn't mess up my order. It doesn't seem to matter if you order online or at the speaker, they will give you the wrong one and by the time you sit down to eat it you realize you got screwed. I'm just going to start going to a different location despite this one being so much closer.\n\nAdvice to management: I understand fast food employees probably quit like once a month but I am begging you to change the training program or something. I've worked in restaurants before, it's possible to make mistakes but there is no excuse for giving the wrong food every. single. time. Something's wrong with your service and at this point I cannot just blame the poor kids working the drive through window, it goes beyond them. Get it together or else y'all deserve to lose business"",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Brenton MacAloney"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUig2sQh5qDAy1aKdhdCkZM5DFCBhmz7cmHmINmJQWdF6WKnSxgA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100"",""Rating"":1,""Description"":""Bought $26 of food on the app and it was ready fairly quickly.   The chicken was fairly good. The fries and macaroni and cheese was cold.  In fact, I think the mac and cheese was not freshly cooked.  The cheese was all lumped together and very unappetizing.  The worst part was we wanted to eat there and I asked for three glasses for water, but the employees were rude about it and refused to give us a cup.  I just bought $26 of food and you can't give me a small cup for water?  Clearly they don't want anyones business here."",""Images"":null,""Whe