ually great. A lot of food.\nGuacamole for the table was good. A tad bland. Very large portion, despite 4 eaters, we had enough to take home.\nLunch time service was good n quick."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2yWqrF7Fn_6PK4Ll5DqEfv8Useycu6g1KB26qmnPfFXuHLEfXQBYA_3_Fd8qOU2IZz5Th10a-PEkzi3JJ1tEzAonBD13iTeDhCp9FBSfD1Cz_hsTs4AuJLUooyEw1PxU47R1KW=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3MjwOWz1JqPVeQE0JNfnzH7aAWzn5aNeWiRwOMQFjTE12HKgTM4KxSxXUdHbM2f20489ne3K15qyXCGK3TxCSr0O4ghOXXXCHyxVeRj-ojgqISW3Rk0z_057m2RnvR8gpSrS0D=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0KwZQdvD6cO3Hj5UP9OOR0Q2Rm79ZgtzEJ8Z0TFlVS_-8TG2bGujQB-0JoCr1zqim2gX4rVY0sFsQCqTICyLJtHpz67jjRbOLAQvaRixkfDnnpiraIFVdNMThIEixwRE36wa4=k-no""],""When"":""2023-11-2""},{""Name"":""Monique"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKhEYK3edCPyhe5Wa86cyswUV0G2g6rGYTgLoTEAUfzN15vLTw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""I used to come here all the time with my coworkers. I always got the Crab Stuffed Salmon\nGrilled salmon stuffed with lump crabmeat and lemon butter. Served with white rice and veggies. It was soooo good! Also enjoyed their chips and guacamole. I need to visit soon."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Cruisinforfulltime"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZOyqhz5WcVIyJ8GIEgV2b6rHmRqkPu3IFrv0YtzAf0EMqOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":4,""Description"":""A Laurel staple. Very good food and service in this restaurant (real old timers probably recall this used to be a Howard Johnsons, as was the adjacent hotel) located in the median between the US Route 1 North and South - bound lanes near Main Street.\n\nThey have good complimentary chips \u0026 salsa, which they refill if needed. The salsa is pretty good - the occasional large bit of onion or pepper indicates it’s made in house.\n\nShared 2 chimichangas - we each had half of the shredded beef (good) \u0026 the grilled chicken which had a great flavor.\n\nTraditional margarita was pretty potent and tasty.\n\nAlways good service with a prompt kitchen."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2NMZiRJ0paT_ON5_JB9maLFuPAYkqH-inEmoYkgk_DElAJc3AYoK_4hpIsmLDTy5VkXe6U3Qj8gMO7-wlfEVgUPj3HmFsHzJEshXtIu7-tpAr2R_2kiMZWpPZwAo6gBLJb2to5=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1AWEZmd7MkEaFtdwYAX9jDkKPqJ1ykm5jvBK0zKPD0CX9GQQEAgQDoXwFZ-3ftZKSeTPlcYyXFtIvWMqfmI9BRbWV7skVFKd-ePQF0lUr63R4958YAA_WD39gj0ENZ0puWguvTAg=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn18FEW-7HCy5LcT-N1_H6O4Q83nz2hf2GdY51Jy_elOcp0vO2r0VWPJ0xiwPeGNYSDUOT7U7XIWIBa1yt1OIRAAyP-90RJOn5fMstr3a4ZpZBg6lKlyjyLqxzqOA8ObZHPS78Eo=k-no""],""When"":""2024-4-18""},{""Name"":""Dversch"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLBBUL8UxBl0diAqbAjp-GNKtrnITic2XeMp956MFrgkQ0AuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Stayed at a nearby Hotel. Stop for nachos chips and dip. The food was surprisingly good so we ordered some takeout and decided to come back the next day and again the day after. The prices are reasonable and the wait staff is friendly and efficient. The atmosphere is clean. Overall an excellent experience."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3YmNSuMJs33Rh5JYHlDknihZbuL4egD2K_8bUfWNVOldr6TU2_D7_6Leo5GmRJZ4fXmkw2QhhGssp0s1zGSchwmb2tPABCAw_oRgw8f5hIcgbln21qGA2ipz8uMti35Lp7u3tC=k-no""],""When"":""2025-5-25""},{""Name"":""Kris S"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJGf6-uZznxlsttZVwgE3XGGcBizIeftNWE_gkDe-hDRmR1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""This was our first time and here and will definitely make this one of our go to spots!!! Great service, great food, nice size portions. Everything was amazing from the appetizers, to the entrees and the margaritas were all flavorful and delicious. Free fresh tortilla chips and house made salsa and the homemade guacamole were also amazing and the prices were very reasonable."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3v2mbbw-o6NJMVcAqGsiqdIowlzZooyVJo-o178waR7BR0PqXq47uIQ24xGr9xSMUTrkTRxkH4qsbUYNSzDrsEx5-t8onAnyzLSAqFGNiV4BGdkAtpliQznKa6r7pW0Y3Kd6iN5A=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2_Q7ridjXXkqovkGOhChzhzfjSeu5soZ--Tnr39ew7IVq8Lk9ewIO7TZdVmHVWKYHQNddZoCVoHKHCCrWKdAQCDx-b0vSkK7n0fnERuslCqXz_bUtG6Sw8tg45iGYKRGUqk5rl=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3ghR4xHYH-HFpG4xJ6moOzSWNqVVBV9KY1wk-SJ89CBcPhJAiU0LZ669EyByK4llrmJhK6MCu1se4AWXJQJ_ksllvu15WcvC-i5ECR9XquOf0-vaAieoQSZN1C0cCB6n0jXWh7tQ=k-no""],""When"":""2021-4-10""}]",null,
