8rYRAVN8O06DS3UHYFn060Hlr0ZJp-3ke3_MnYTx=k-no""],""When"":""2025-2-27""},{""Name"":""Jose Montano"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLbHfYO9gk4tJY7zax0PIwDHO4qRyCTdTQF1EEAa3GeyHooVw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Very great food here I've been to this place about 3 times now and the food has always met my standards for authentic Mexican/Salvadorean food. The 1st and 2nd time I got the bean and cheese pupusas. But, this 3rd time I decided to get the birria pizza and it was amazing. A bit pricey but trust me it's worth it you can feed a whole family with it. I am very impressed as a San Jose native I would've never thought a place like Maryland had such good Mexican cuisine."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Eating With Sun"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVP3AvDOch2A-6gXyZE7XD-UlXAdwEimo4b4_wu7fxHqhVNpyzC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100"",""Rating"":3,""Description"":""The food was delicious. My birria tacos were DELICIOUS and worth the $16 ticket price. However, the side of rice \u0026 beans was an additional $9. The waitress was very kind and accommodating. The food all around was great."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn24RJJx2noFPM9pJ27538plqT7ugFZxmM_UF9avxuSEa-HxQz480clsCjpqK37t0H0gYGWcnDnbWHXVoypkLcwzJfgSsbY9coK9x1UyV2SyKYKhue7c5UwmJI7H8i8cpncHtakhog=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1jbrlswDqJ2t84sFuknJcyjdIuyPyftjgZhyp6aBgSDJeFDvjPrdlW_OVB0ljFtt8MIg-JRIzsxWlSrYDLVsK7cqX7S8UJUhJiIjoD_vRZrTcrwhPO4J08GSj7jArAw8sPhceY=k-no""],""When"":""2024-12-6""},{""Name"":""Hayden Brooke Duke"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTgBIgmqiDzY9DmsKYKSdd0TAvTQ1oOCSVsd3MCgkOlv7ztuKs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Ay Dios Mio! The food here is amazing. I had the Baleadas with steak and it was excellent, some of the best food I've had in a while. The only points I took off were for the atmosphere since the music was blaring, as in I had to do wait for the singer to take a break to complete my sentence. That does not take away from the food or the incredible service."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Ben"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUowFkozuxsXqB1b5PFgt-8Kq8qMVgKvTL_k3AaZBpmO99xql2WCg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100"",""Rating"":4,""Description"":""$12 burrito was huge and served quickly. Friendly service and fresh food.\n\nThe food and the service are worth coming back for, but I have issues:\n* charged $3 for a bottle of water. That is one way to make money, but I'm not a fan.\n* Loud music. Luckily I was eating alone and not trying to talk to anyone.\n* Flashing lights. The space is a mixture of bar and restaurant, but bright flashing colored lights are distracting."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1L6Htie0NzG01LR96iPNd2LoI19WwNJMPUSNgQrWlVzRpOXSNtAlh3Khl7aUMjyxLiVIGZHngtgVVjK_sQ-AlQeAez_O1rmMpJ5J3-LeoHaNZkXyyKSkE6WZul1FWS3fybMrbqZQ=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn13cqaslVd6pZ5yrfW7HWwjsA4-3O1JHudNjWAh_Yv0oRbfxdJUTTZFr25-mADVLtyUDQmVMls9fgSN0_kykZ92cIdf2qjdme4kwurZryO1LH6X42BjyECsRr318dEXztZCHkWD=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn36tCrZWA2NkvOZaphM2PExNZ_hWuCV1TabxdekiFGt5hiMJxobKTFIoDCgJZLEmSVWhbWz_2x7dperbBoMoEX7EpG0HNiPIckNHQ5kbrcWRN7NowHTOaIQRTUwPM3hjrzZEgtllg=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1F740TUbpkA7NbZFnTEOde2cXn87voIZVm-SrSLWIEPf8heHLqbhIn4sY0Ov7ZLyDU7mybHCUHrEZz7zyf7K_tRRE58rDkGZV7CiXKB9N7jnOnQi_xgCWLTB1o4zMEuFReDXbs=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0xGH9GAUTOZR6HiuLeJ91XRAU5pAZladBlXWEimoe3drf6_1GLSw7IuJ4RuQgm445ZkqoQCAjAOvT0NwyfY5_M9EqjCWIRwvvb4EYfNzTvKhWgwZjzgDpMlrlQ9VQPNkS1nXiy=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0HtSHtWVmaRah3LAOfRkweDL3SY16mqUP98cOjlb5ypx--t78hn7z9dg8oVP-Y2qj4JCCrbpYurWhk1rinGBowyhaOZeynzvA9PG7AmQWmbSY-mikRfgQr3FpcdXyxbIQicMYx=k-no""],""When"":""2023-3-30""},{""Name"":""JC"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKuhsYy0EQOFe9xfJO4D5pWc-NE5JuPOnABcoydQqCZpsJKvA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""I ordered a beef soup, DELICIOUS. The tortillas are made of corn and you can savour the homemade, the best beef soup I've ever eaten👌"",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Zachary"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEgCIpKBbzJS5trxf5HRl-y2qpfv8uRaVmjvaDIXPfX3-6VYWVxg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":1,""Description"":""I placed an order for 60+ tacos via grub hub around 930 this morning so I can feed my staff at 1230 for a business lunch. Order was over 220 dollars. I get a call from grub hub at 1130 saying the restaurant cancelled my order. I called your restaurant and the girl said the manger said \""no more grub hub\"". Ok that's fine but why did you wait to let me know an hour before I needed it. So then I tried to place the same order with the girl over the phone and she says she couldn't do it. I took my $220 order to el patron which is right down the street.\n\nI've worked in Laurel for 4 years now and I loved getting my tacos from you guys. I will not be returning again or give you any of my business again. You lost a big customer."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Mischiefox"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWW61GO-L6iX7b6D5GqN0bcARDODr02BgZkAEEQLDU7fKoUpMyBkg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100"",""Rating"":4,""Description"":""Seems like a big popular local Mexican restaurant. Loud music and delicious food.\n\nNo fountain drinks and the horchata tasted differently than I expected. They do serve the wet style burritos here. Not my preference, but it still tasted great regardless. The pupusas were definitely as you'd expect. They were great.\n\nWould definitely eat here again"",""Images"":null,""When"":""""}]",null,
