r."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1jRreEjCud6nylT-Kz3jRQr-tf0WyWNHrbyjIUNrrzi3gdhYjL-PJ_awIqeP9LEvm3RJnXwqOtlftYpiwTGMH85Ai9BZhMplXnyDOvBZMVFz9sWnsCdSwNZo5HbmUHWtYvcm9jyqBjbdeE=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1yO5VAySKkb9lmQZcYxXbvAQsLI2xv0DY9HSnScki308qzDzPbR7qJGh-QAv143Frs7_4-7b119jBXsfLIw9gUItYVqyJqG_FirI-tZkYpyybHONiGP0KwdHsYerJLVEiR20-labL7YmpJ=k-no""],""When"":""2025-11-16""},{""Name"":""Lily"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7CHBzywI63rB8XfhUTowzEr777m4Z7LrjcS-40r0oC7ZMRIiw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Amazing! I tried the banana bread latte and the vegan breakfast croissant. Both were super delicious and it was so cool to have vegan options for breakfast. The staff were super sweet and the environment was very welcoming and clean. I will definitely be returning when I'm in the area! One thing to note, they don't take Discover so plan to use a different card."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0mulOG6K-tJMy7dyi8k9Lye26HsRuj7cC7g17ykfxD8VXfQ2FZBUVSkNV6TAfV1eXSIHgb2PhMXPvh26wffJqVWxUE484Ao2rcBcFDoc1eb0N09KVk_u9D-7Sv-ToBYh7hSXIAMiH1yYo3=k-no""],""When"":""2025-9-28""},{""Name"":""Phace Artistry"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhqJl3qJPcZNbhBXwVMoRBfcu_GrAVts28N0Rld9dova8Kx6dp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":4,""Description"":""Love Life Café Review ☕️💻\nDefinitely a nice atmosphere to sit, have coffee, or bring your laptop to get some work done. I ordered the Dirty Chai with banana flavoring — it was about $10 and tasted pretty good! I probably should’ve added an extra shot for a stronger kick, but overall it was a great experience. I’ll definitely be visiting again!\n\n#LoveLifeCafe #CoffeeLovers #CafeVibes #DirtyChai #MiamiEats #CafeReview #WorkAndSip #CoffeeBreak"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2jfEIqEYVzVT9-iIdBeMXDNuhz0YOdSjfxKbMnHXxbyzGVC1