 these wraps 🤤"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn32MKWHewQEkEF2AXuk0kNX1kXxURvNnocPr0DdXa44IDVvhc1z9EXy22s44AgehYzWee288WNtWBQnXhxGCa6Z763LjlVqUGwVy4xCsNp-4k1MrZS5dZtIJw9qTDv4-txfnUHAWV72P6b2=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn25h5EsfH1wf_VFq21H-K9xQz2BaUKtfcH17MoT3ev0JQqVQG1KLyocb8BT6VDrHiXtQBwz682L8aW2WEho5Z2DuzSal2yODdQ_R_Pqr6cgghnzCIu3gfR_Y953l12pxAYsZFAX6xpQDivn=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3f65m4ncR89KquCw5mtIhs_KJWyPAIa8wlChDLszMIwaCdjZUEvHYLMtqH6zt3sfjjpO5SlvXsx3c-ezRhpr0UPT3fQrs0bl6uhrkPcTG_XSzTGLl1qwIeI_lBEYfKXwe0IrghGXeb1bH8=k-no""],""When"":""2025-9-27""},{""Name"":""Anne-Olive N"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI2hIs58vnrsKcuNb792G1dC3zPFYYHaxGN40FKw-J3cptTudnP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100"",""Rating"":4,""Description"":""TikTok sent me to get this suya wrap! Def order ahead if you don’t want to wait 20-30 minutes to get your food. This wrap is $20 which is kind of hefty, but does come with a bunch of meat. However, the fries are stale and cold which was disappointing. The suya is seasoned but spicy so beware of that!"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn34rwvH6J2iagSJLORU8B2IJup8UV5NCQuTOudDEjS2SiQGwkZxtYx1siFn7SHu_2A-KFbBmYRmGOiPWEAmonHVl03xmF0WyP-6Of1PW9KftuHU00mOBy2lVJ4xmb1Ehx4Hvo0543bcS60=k-no""],""When"":""2025-10-29""},{""Name"":""Hilda Tah"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYDDAmBfAx0jVqwKLYIOItTvSbt9bTILfDm6MUh1y_rkCTeuU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Prime grill has one of the best African food I’ve ever tasted. If it’s your first time the suya wrap is good but try the wings, fish or cassava leave"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn16F-7RkbHyxhF58IGyxdzEKhb5inBxDqLoivyiYcZkBkJ6ikIO2tJjwwxYO_7N55OHSNauvZXg0as4kZmAudye4pv9aVDEZUkwUUQhM3Gej69X2PCYhMj1ZNIG85rkeahF5nRnPg0274bw=k-no""],""When"":""2025-11-9""},{""Name"":""James Cloyd"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL_vgOUyZuqdX3mGVd_iCqHaS2dD1yT1RllD5-qWfCuiwmEXg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":2,""Description"":""The food is tasty, which is why I kept giving this place more chances. Unfortunately, the service has been consistently slow, and the wait times don’t feel accurately communicated.\n\nEven when you call ahead or order online, it seems like the preparation doesn’t really start until you arrive. On my last visit, I ordered and paid for suya about 30 minutes before getting there, and then still had to wait another 30 minutes once I showed up.\n\nI enjoy the food, but after that experience, I probably won’t be returning."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Dorothy Obianuju"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGRJH61gGcwwlYeU2KPV01Dud2V3s83oigDxaD7LvxKjNStxla=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Discovered this place on Tik Tok and I am so glad I did! This place has become my new favorite spot! The Suya wrap is very flavorful and very filling! The Suya wrap has an option of plantains or fries. I chose plantains. Though they were good, it only came with three plantains. For the price, I think we should get more than three. I paid $19.99 (pre-tax and tip). Not pictured, but the Jollof rice and Suya are also very good, especially with the liquid hot sauce! In person ordering is through the kiosk. Parking on a Sunday is very tight due to the restaurant being located next to a church. Other days of the week,there are plenty of parking. Service can be slow but mostly because they’re making the food fresh. Overall, definitely a restaurant that I will be coming back to!!"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2zk0_M1odL1yqCqNkBPX52Mu8ILQpNUzdxYSFVrYrQDicD3Wbw8MY0y5nlSO0m3vje5gAdqwH8mK99-Mszk5CLJt6Lipwq6Y16nx_ypSopm1mg6_x5Q4LvK0WoG5wkzUQb-DY8-0f8d0Jw=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Q0356WPsq9ltuWmug59B3m