",""name"":""Pets"",""options"":[{""name"":""Dogs allowed outside"",""enabled"":true}]}]","[{""Name"":""Phace Artistry"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhqJl3qJPcZNbhBXwVMoRBfcu_GrAVts28N0Rld9dova8Kx6dp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":4,""Description"":""I stumbled upon this place while on a walk with a friend, and I’m glad we did! I took my crepe to go, so I didn’t get to enjoy it fresh, but the flavor was okay once reheated. The ambience was lovely, and the owner was super pleasant — plus, it’s Black-owned, which I love supporting. Definitely a cute spot to bring your laptop, grab a drink, and vibe out for a bit.\n\n#CafeVibes #BlackOwnedBusiness #CrepeLovers #CoffeeAndChill #SupportLocal #CuteCafes #WorkAndSip"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn19ArTRRmO3AY9KGUKUsRufbqxmUgKrh6lp1gkcqgFtk2eHtv-Y42Y1En43oFockZATGXDBMs8y05c6M1tEwV0yfs2MHY_Cj6WAR2no5uvr0lP0L-1gI1Gh2OM-SnGdu41hhvjyfRTEOMu1=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2gZ0WTienpc8b0hzMoNCKQl8ScVrT3_6faeRswjAHgQyCpqzZQ6A2VHdEzik-bGalcDohVweLYJkKblrhGBBOnUs1REDV60qhnJINwevFjuHKL1cjpRM1WlFGhNJKzNUkznHSveICn0H8=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2HXFI7uxl8VanwI-96v9uFdOTorZq__1fj4faAxksEl0jy626X1_Vx9B2vUGwxjSMN-ukB-pLgMqbdb0gjgaFpTJaRX4piFweW_nbv4TZM69yHWMcALr8HqaSNQ1okPVl3Sr6BqcppJ1Jc=k-no""],""When"":""2025-10-24""},{""Name"":""Darryl Lemons"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL4SFgZvIAdLYvLCUXyJI7K-BQtZFlU6HI02WgXtaeeJDYZPg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":1,""Description"":""I ordered two waffles. The employee at the counter was unsure how to process the order and had to request assistance from the manager. Upon receiving my order, I found that the waffles were burnt on the outside and undercooked on the inside (please see attached photos for reference)."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3VQBTeKKCttCQddHxC0WEFxD-JUHf9MeN5-lIxVa3OWUeT-jXsIFU2sK6L85sEcWX6gwZfwhisvO3fxFXejrlpdgPIo_Pb4Bjmdw49YD9pg-8QCTW5jQycV8NYxlfwfSe5hV-Im-40QOI=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3dCcywWZ8fC3Aa1jP9AgHoAmZbCr3KIYh_6yXXOlBcm_2Dn8_S-2wfJDyDpVa6zW-99056aEd--IBgCqNttMJRM5923F4-ur0DSgGe_lZsgKTegWKqWtwmXHznCIRFR0lD7VpKZNfHP2Nl=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0ooRj68Ym7JqCpbFWDBsyFkMFidUfywnS86DVJux3zUvm6eSIkKmeXK2L5PGEvgGoiNl17ExmhPrPrbEmBt6ZO5uji7xbL87LGdmdRX0yxTyZKIeRAlMCIxsQekqW4w-IN2QYjda4ZbNM=k-no""],""When"":""2026-1-10""},{""Name"":""GaryC"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI3X3xXL2K7VKWZ0GlTYcyteFDufoQNyV19z6Qr9Yiatg9rMw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""I learned of this restaurant from InstaGram. I was politely greeted by Remi, who took my order for a sweet crepe. The aroma from the cooking of my crepe had me anxiously waiting to taste it. It was the sweet scent of pancake batter which is my favorite breakfast food. I simply devoured the crepe, made with various fruits, while chatting with Remi. She was very pleasant and polite. She not only made me feel welcomed, but it was as if we were sitting in her home, chatting over a meal. The restaurant seating consist of hi-top tables and chairs which were very comfortable to me. I found the restaurant to be be very clean and and well-lit. There is a beautiful mural on one the wall that I admired.Prices of crepes I felt were reasonable and worth every cent. If you want a really good and tasteful crepe, I would suggest you to stop by and try one. I only noticed there was  street parking and it was not metered. I will certainly be a repeat customer. Keep up the great job, Remi."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Linnea Neuber"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIw8mZB39aBa7rxyENDdl68cI7C2n1s1Wt8KnNTCrxjaI0ROg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""We found this place randomly online and I’m glad we did! We’ve been making it a point to support small businesses this year and I’ve been craving crepes recently. My husband and I both ordered a sweet and a savory to check out the selection. The woman who helped us took the time to walk us through the menu and everything we ordered was delicious.\n\nThe place was very clean and had a cute vibe. Highly recommend if you love crepes and caramel lattes!"",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Michael Marana"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtD6XlEpa2ehIqcvmJhxiT_1VaALqbHeTT8OY1BGrD9f9Bb-ol=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100"",""Rating"":2,""Description"":""I got a breakfast crepe and a Bavarian crepe. Unfortunately the menu didn't have descriptions of anything so I had to go by the pictures. It took a while to make, nothing memorable about the crepes, they were a little more soggy than I would have preferred. Strangely, the breakfast crepe had some sort of Italian seasoning sprinkled on it, with a spicy sauce. I would have preferred just a traditional breakfast crepe. The vibe was strange, the decor was like a chic wine bar, but the crepes were served on plastic plates with plastic utensils. There were high top tables and couches with tiny tables; it was hard for my toddler to eat comfortably."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Meena J"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL2z8AB3nkM9PYyTx34JRuPnGPcomucoFf6JMXb-4fgP1hcew=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Second time eating here; great service, crepes were fresh and delicious and so welcoming! this is my new and favorite study spot. Even made a mimosa for me despite it not being included on the menu--love! As a crepe lover and wine connoisseur, this restaurant is now one my faves in Laurel :)"",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Amy Caballero"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfdlyMT84kadeg8iyvokSnEut0WdN7E6GCkG_XR6CJv_dCFRpo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""I randomly found this place because I was craving a crepe. The crepes are fairly priced for the portion you are given. I got 1 savory and 1 sweet crepe. The savory crepe I got was the shroom and root veggies. I liked that it had a variety of veggies with some cheese. The sweet crepe I got was the Bavarian crepe. I liked that it was with yogurt and just sweet enough. Not too heavy. I recommend trying this place out! They also serve ice cream :)"",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""kalina35"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvF2kVAndhXHLlqXXjhfCgityiGc-4RS2AWBXa4MDmMdVwPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Absolutely delicious. Freshly made with fresh ingredients; chicken tender stewed,moist, well seasoned, veggies cooked perfectly, crepe was soft and with a nice chew. I got the chicken and schrooms crepe, and my daughter ordered the TEC crepe (turkey bacon,egg, and cheese). Spicy sauce is sweet and then the spicy hits you on the backend. Definitely going back. Check out the menu and see for yourself.\nThe young lady there makes them when ordered and she was the only one behind the counter. Be patient please."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""}]",null,
