r, was excellent. Jennifer was very helpful with helping us decide which dish to choose and very friendly. We loved sharing a couple stories with her and hearing her story as well.  So happy we chose Cuba De Ayer Restaurant tonight, we will definitely be back."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1czaKrvdWfy84S1VlEITCxnvMAPK4W6HtnR9I4Sxj0LUQYc8llhKlMN4iTdNY5a6NC5c7TeGV2V3QsILj0Wpo2Z5BddQ3a6gnDNKAGDyw0gIy9vALUpYvM8tKQjMpcfgdq_P8Z9OOfUB_9=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0wc1fUmpFdXbYEagspHhwRhJcuqXBuxk1OFEY_5JouLPt7PvsnBFxj6Ngu0JJwTT8CYMdp7n_JPXIWM3Q-YhwerVnbN4p5qFMkW9DS8ydquKyrIPUtl7L-8l-BFqmh6gRGNgQOLreBkMw0=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0tAJ0xz4IId3kjdZ722Jn2PV60MYqxmK36GfiqnV74JdzR7kjB8xzNr4oM1bM4kHv4hhsauiY5E6GTX5QpSqRzIABfTLNr-qvIsLcray9fUn6mBJ6-_5qmWsJysgvf5YLhkeFzpYUdwg0=k-no""],""When"":""2026-2-7""},{""Name"":""marlo z."",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDEcPbdUSdtLp05RQAzsCZnHcXI6tI69UVHdQqlk5F2pw9e9RK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Wife and I had a very nice early dinner here on a Wednesday night.\nThe staff are very friendly and we were seated quickly and our food was also prepared promptly.\n\nWe are not real familiar with Cuban cuisine but both enjoyed our dishes (one beef and one chicken).  Each came with a side of rice and beans and plantains.  My wife got her rice and beans “combined”, while I got mine separate. Also comes with plantains and I got the sweet ones and she got the crispy.  We both agreed that we liked the sweet ones better.\n\nTopped it off with a delicious  Tres Leches desert.\n\nThe dinning areas are nicely configured with separation between the different rooms and also some space between the tables, which is nice.\n\nAlso, we were surprised to have a musician playing on a Wednesday night, which was a nice addition."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2pPzkBCdvLAbiteodh