ed aged beef and fish was impressive.  I had the 60day dry aged burger - and it quite possibly was one of the best burgers I’ve ever had.  The beer was also great.  I’m a big fan of West Coast IPAs, and I feel they missed the mark on that beer - but the hazy IPAs were very flavorful and delicious.  I would highly recommend Jailbreak Foodworks if you’re in the area.  Excellent!!"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Zbk55gpQW3JocBnJU67I2f2JU56KUOtU8EWTqRXzn3AnoBQd2nyrO0-PdByI_DWZ5ct13vSFAIZNoH-3F1gYZqCVa873DYYaeaRW52zGHopcRclxqUEuaD5cmmam3r6EReIiLZQDDLsS8=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn25N532z6s1yZqMVAhZztqwnNOx4dCzBQRtjHI-J4Hxwz-8OBKFgq_kOtLFmp77RUORA6OapyZIsQF8knNQZ5STJKDR_Zw4-IRJB9xi8snIiydThO44VGk7lJC6y3iz3B6DK6UCcwr65Xs=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2VbRB3kvsWX_bRLkgFm0xDu9WCddZB71XtbDnU0_LlRwA4HX2K0CB738tJYClPFF9kgD7ig11EP3NCdlIkH9l99ByuzTd3Fm_06nmxc2k4RCbMCbGpe9DuE6bSJ3ImbczjBVZE61vTkhHt=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1uRs1eCT7jHY85Spu4IASkcjEjkqbNE7w5qemlh4UkmmR6tii84PPQ9ydSS3X-oD8Gg4rwdSEA4Ij1lYRAIknoGOvFvyoy-R_e5f_3WSoIJ9aLmxffvUGGqLP2WDd0gd4d-q3SdrhLXbo_=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2OclKoyCeOx46LIyHaX2_WVdE6hmbvri7WBzG5PyimmogJjTu_1tivhqahz47Zgc_kXM-u1hRFqwmCZp2Z3Rzp-vBUzInLrgD7-yfsaZX988665vlR2WIY_leTSREHLz4AFuBox5tlCAA=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Q1grJ4uGKSFCpSjBNRcZ45QlRu8tmfF-e33BxbVRNbFa_rdeAxyRPBF7CfoU9OT2ogsMOyuv88qmgeQnJkREgzCheEvj3KZ9Wlu5__gH38jQuPsQxaWDgJhfHmY6A3js-AQZ3aYUKHagW=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn16SJsI0rFDs_fg0BLCOV1tMH-F3HzWuKXq6Xs_qpMS7SX6-isdCyt7OD8bEA4SBysUNK2u0lJYEjlb2sSjegzfd_JMnufdV60H6jTGdcx1re7J0WNYKmxnaSDmFBDQYGjf_2l9hSxpxqaM=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1mLXAkmX1uCwgpCyyHZiTmSTaGNbiMj7vR_pDpk3-iz0PDQMq6JE6NLlOnAsSehh59ncfzrNQnDK55Pfqic8C0crHO1Nw-vJLCDE_MDIJCb7QKWR-uC0v2tgDhlXofCaUeaWdpsvEVd627=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0twCkEWnM9tL-1fw2bNAGtph5FPTN-0OTiLer1xj3Fs4msgJTzAUzGuLofHg5Bw4wcPVYaC7GrwKWcVIfD3SUxsAGJTUVj_IurWMgC4dUqil9R7Q46ORYpdt7-ElxqyI2RQH_Uki2tuM1r=k-no""],""When"":""2026-2-26""},{""Name"":""George Junca"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWjniWFIY9IwXnEUI3_pix5WwPdnM40S-T67CVtEv0ZuFcELDJuYA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""I have been to a LOT of breweries and have to say the food here ranks among the top, not just in quality and flavor but variety as well. The (Korean) steak frites was very flavorful, the jerk chicken cheesesteak was a great find, and could not get enough of the Parmesan fries. The beers of course are great with also quite the variety from the more popular Lady Friend (and variations) hazy IPA to the super robust Dusk til Dawn stouts. Staff was super friendly as well."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1MfIKaqZD38H4YbHilg2OE8Yux5hZaannCTYIok5O2_tFhqDvOv69dSxk2kl5Oxm1_3kaajwNHgBSUPAP2DHt5PLiAXGDCXF8JDl2gb9kH-CzEWZDu_j5OEy4gMGGyS14OrEbR3N3YRZ2N=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn04gouIaNr8OF4Kj_UWdp5419dCt04G1c8-_aX3Ju3myZL3rgYXus3CeQUCb5Ce_5z4Hri4y3eB12cxkcJ0QKhLCvkcnfoA23Y9v7sxEOpSPmnlPhCxrG_M_O2VqRpK58U5rn9aRJ1OPAGX=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1SN56tK5d5sb86Rdo2G0Ihq2rmRid0RJLn5rn6q9-_qqHwGDC382tNeLbjiAP2jI5Beoh_GscYDYeUgJjwzY-CKDvwP3EmqKM1RtqHd2AduF_Fi4OBu0g0KO7KuaRGoy0lBxgIOFx1Y69C=k-no""],""When"":""2026-2-13""},{""Name"":""Greg"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVweZfPlYczkKo0y8pwb8PyWDbMcD0t3skCAkH3GF_6QomK5Yg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Excellent experience . Been coming here for years. They constantly surprise me with new brews. Now they are surprising me with food options. I had the palmetto cheese dip. Best I have ever had outside of South Carolina. And the Boats \u0026Hose beer was so good that I bought a 6 pack for home."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3LqDsvqGq6HbiejU0cVhReih4DxkF7S9eW3eq9lyN04uSVJ2UN7lqDKgwp1mxvCp96BZJ03YqsWoPbHijSWPUYLWqWerbCRJ7zD-4hW1_bI7IYkEfThWwhWMlLMMJ0M1cvmXVlQTXrwh49=k-no""],""When"":""2026-3-9""},{""Name"":""Jake Dustin"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKaEF1QYIuh9Ho_nT60NDgcFJCdDVhFzvaAhI1VkIDzb1esog=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""I had a really great experience. It is still a brewery at the end of the day, but the dry aged steak that I had and the way it was served was at the level of a high-end restaurant. It was cooked and seasoned perfectly and I'm a very picky steak eater. The beer was also exceptionally good would definitely come back here again."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1jAi-HzVE29XTPy3lG8jx1X_rzi330e3_HO3tnoKMyWw29Ht3UkVB-pwaw3qpBziAx6Wfdw9WjcSO76c-4gPQmC-j8a62nVvaN3JI9BF3qUr4_rF4CWmul-xF1q-SWPUW0YxvRVB2njg1i=k-no""],""When"":""2026-1-4""},{""Name"":""Lola Ajayi (Lola)"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLNIwDP2Optjd8wl_7O1hIhbAV3INqebozdD0of1rognwW56dC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""This spot has been on my list for the last 3 or 4 years. I finally decided to go when I saw it was right next door the auto shop I took my car to recently.\n\nThe staff here was very nice. I had a several questions for 3 different staff members I encountered and they were all happy to answer my questions and had good energy.\n\nThe burger I got was unique and very much a craft burger. They have a lot of dry-aged meats here (including their burger), and I thought it was good and still a little juicy. The fries were average fries. I also got an orange crush that was also good, a cider, and sampled their slushies. They have a strawberry bourbon slushie I really liked. I would have ordered it but it was strong and I had already gotten the crush, so I’ll just have to come back for it. The other slushie was a coffee one and I’m not a huge coffee person, but if you like coffee, you’d probably like that.\n\nChildren are allowed here until 7 pm I believe. Unfortunately, they do not do tours (anymore). I’d like to see them bring this back because I’m always interested in the process and also hearing about how things are produced.\n\nYou order food on one side (and can also order cocktails on that side too) but the beers and others are ordered on the brewery side. You’re able to open a tab on either side though and it will be connect, so you don’t have to do multiple transactions."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn17VPPHlZfRVsvqCJePzROgoPJsuInXjUPzi_cHOw2ez1IjCf9oPfxFXunUg5sq8Ty5TDqmwYbITSumr_AcJ03eETHeJ70lYxCZQG1Ab2DB0QQG2t7iCn5irBiOeHIKyGsIhrs37p95SdwX=k-no""],""When"":""2025-10-29""},{""Name"":""Maggie Baer"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVG0dhfo-U94KFB4gQ26M176-tDyQ7LLQ4Txo0YDyzVeU901Emy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":4,""Description"":""An awesome place with a great vibe! There’s a couple arcade games and tvs to watch games. The brewery is large so there’s plenty of space for small and large parties. I highly recommend the truffle fries and the Rum Punch Funk - subtle amount of coconut with other fruity flavors. Everything was delicious! No one under the age of 21 after 7pm."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1ZuKDxlQB7JU75BPqWT5vqYE2_HiN-DQqV0zS3pGmb5swBMVBnvr68w3NKuoUDXPT8VMDh4UWhkH0uo4kipTFq2LvA2LPoYJ_lRtcbtJWJbqqkyZqYDq5qRDmWXclBigF0Qfh73EvHDZYP=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0JN13mlhXimczt6XqrFfDYI81KswIXdHeiOC4P0pEvac9yGjxeSZUdsWIrR920T16uvEx6vgJ69Z23CL_nFgkbPMfsl4CcmfqCGN_3sr3byvxRRgdoMBLpA8KX6XEUz1Nd_EzTqh_cVSFV=k-no""],""When"":""2025-8-24""},{""Name"":""Joshua Boster"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJJSMVGUFeSzCMTkw2jqTBU3HHT0lRDQXJqEe1nPWwTb5Zq5aCX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Great service, great beer. The pretzel and fries were amazing. Note that the chicken is all dark meat which is not my preference and wasn’t clear on menu. They have a really cool vibe, arcade games, dry aged meat. We will definitely be back"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2zSIkUSyIOn_9mRym0zB9BiL3Aibiywb8i8DvIgcWM1NBDcog8weWMsNgj_amsadgJNTBlxYlyjfWtI6zZWuxV4OAok6MXps6vIZW3e4i-UrJBktsLi9i9cU7qjrxkGejngu7fXf6oQlKY=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0vTnsrp3NrteD83YhYKntVy2saO_VytxB4Os80F50OXEGhJOhjnzfbOjshkvyJOIjM3po1hm6uYH50QKEox0NO3qtYaqnV2EayyuzSY-sK9JuNWBlPIcOEoS4fDaYrgMYluvEwyQg6ipU=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn181oVS1lYF4RacdA-fKofDT5nEJJeI3OLvrrXRxo2mcEAfFqXSUqhZR8X1XkQBmd19IfyJVsCKcsURsoONTh07vDphmXefjghu2rcPgdtr2muWUhmMfmBF3e0hOhw1jZveS1UjSbdj7vHs=k-no""],""When"":""2025-9-12""},{""Name"":""Eric Ferraris"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcEM_Ekge1UkFIvZ08b4rUlSW8EPZkIHkdC0hAokXD_FQMgKc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""It is a must stop every time we come to town. Great food, excellent selection of liquor and beer.  Dry aged meats and fish is one of the best......"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0VuhhnIbONHpMkU4ZIF4aNvTepLF8Uc-9WEdApIuFm1HmW_cq7YO3j26CDsd0_dSJ0BR-tHHeVmtZrptB2k3cqrb6CbROpjyN4KZsiCsX9Xlr3MYN429E3jkYEMABdVRtOROu8JEKQsy3V=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0T9jYurXDb-Tz2WQkvl6sOBL2lDu5US8QRhZbffJOMCZAg-B25YxrmLLbdXvGSNbs_ktRweR48di5Z8G5ApW0XV_ksD_qFCCLBWdZJwzIxUmGec0Ftl4bpYNJMFv1j5iJAWSUxzE1awhc=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0xnoe33LF-ruUkjM_87h4yJWEolJVP167yhMx-BelZWy35nWFSEeQ-9wjDeT1kbRHjQVyWu4pdltx7yKrKdZ2oYVrAfgF-8KejMk-u8gtVyuyS50LYFiGrePzhNWqNN8g4T8A5l3-Kf9U=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0krpFdAiw1GbnEYAOqueHq-4E2McEDMCNfSWzEHTsPQQCTlaDl5MOupBVzaYaVDf35F