leusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2FrAc0_-E_GaZwRHxOMAaNF2JLQiitHnSPUhjnDLyuaYbHe63IvIZ2os2KE_3aoc5JUb2tg6o54aJj2dET8_PDAhsq6Lx0-SBzN0F48kkKTEKn_B4wgPjFEZq3bWvVZY2yxuvCprh8X_Wm=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3OX2UjJ2KzLRdLFyxUndYEQuM515dXY1coJVSxi4PfReTVrt_Z6skdrZL1KUr9MzTP77DkmEFDXWQVRBeeeqEINdIpoJbD7ry3cjyncpgADBesWu1sW5dSM7RZnlsQCkeLLg65YGeUfs1v=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3iPVGzr1U1ekmkiBoEBV4FLPH3BadULf0M5WTAXMxW09sDxmquuAx_xOmquOd64lvEBHx68Cn9NV0NL-C5vTk043eWeP3AkXOZyCyF_5RSPlWUPdmyfQVrx5bzteU9nc2FFrx4GOcdeOjo=k-no""],""When"":""2025-8-12""},{""Name"":""Myranda Stephens - REALTOR"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpu1Yz86WfV1yQvOte_j9JguiEaoH-CqKP2IpPYVf-v-OjtSo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":3,""Description"":""I was excited to try Amber Spice because I heard they had excellent Indian cuisine, which I love. But my experience wasn’t great. Apparently the restaurant closes between lunch and dinner, but the host did not immediately tell me that when I walked in for takeout. So while I was looking over the menu, he abruptly asked me to make a selection before the kitchen closed. I felt rushed. I ordered the Karahi, I believe. It was spicier than I expected, but decent overall. Again, not a great first impression for this restaurant, but perhaps I’ll try again in the future and hope for a better experience."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1ocul7v0rDi70mFgoUfYLxTtysM1QI2DQTww7ArCYKPh8LugTKSfEApOkCU5-whwTQcLn8ssZ3lZ5cwEZJ6kpNzw65IJm1FvPPlkEYxqp474zMCNZBzPlL_avxJEUzmH-tHOme=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0M3ni7lqe15r-oQ8s9Hzv5eV6GWHxdYYls4wEZh-e4t-K02HnNkaRtxm4Xcdqji37bwM_dMQ8vl41YDXc6G6mi1IupeLL4iWua2JXeucHbDRXiUZ3lkCx2_kF5JexYQqUXy5CQ=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn32Y-k1VLRsrWKKqCReX_vy_nRe5-FyXiA3cww6iTfNZZQVsjXNcIWFZFDNgOFYoKH_CDkQhZhAONRj7jDTvwFvfzzeBdmt1X4IN-d34NMW1OuLdg1qy-_DPaT-s4fkG6cV8gs=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1qBaw-ShqdZhAKdDHd3kTy2fsRwW0HOXmhw-yE5rIWO1kNTSPEGbwlQrE5rXQFTfiF0V-NdXqSM25yMMl6m8uEvDAajE5ictWD97iuSWlgtX5Pkdms9IV0q3wMvBBHyUYajJJ9AQ=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1npC-3a4SZX86GN2oo_CUcoM3_RWlW0FCQB1r3JDvtErzFV1cbDLvYpQPJJIQSyFsKn949rUSNIbzc2aAnhEAfPfYCBHiQFYpi4j1QklYmmCJ0Mm54M6jH_pHtZmTjEEGEooA2=k-no""],""When"":""2025-4-9""},{""Name"":""Sara D"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4K4aHCadVsN_MqqpGoSXT8GDtPyMCt77sY4deG80MAGeP_tpkPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":4,""Description"":""I've mainly done take out at this restaurant so I can't really talk about the service, But I've always enjoyed with the food. Food just tastes really good no complaints. But I do have one gripe with this restaurant and that is the cost of a single mango lassi, I think it is beyond crazy that I am paying $6.50 for less than 12 oz, most restaurants will give you a 16 oz at that price. Can I get it that's a cost of food and everything has gone up and things are not as cheap but $6.50 for an 8.5oz to maybe 10 oz cup is crazy. And it wasn't filled to the burn it's because I shook it that it looks like It was filled."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2bVIZdHVPVsyqfzbQXOfGc7xWCT-jHMUbdLJuMey3oGcsgppX9sSDSt9EOVBQeRU7Yi8hm-Ke5r0GrYz-JwdyJIzG53AF4EaUpGDIO8grfCa41cXWlB7_NNTx7wrvyFdm9VwQNIbKWcZEn=k-no""],""When"":""2025-10-27""},{""Name"":""Hayat Hashim"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKxeVHganpCFFeAZbDvhh2zbe-UMmRQIGg-4kcxe4vjhE7eoQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""We are original from NYC - where Indian food has not limits. Food at Amber spice was authentic and delicious. They definitely can compete at a high level of spices and flavor. We are foodies and were pleasantly surprised with the tastes.\nWill be visiting when we are in Maryland again."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3pq4opdTw0_FhG4R_awHkXJBUEPOe8UIUEwuF5iX_e-xOj9yKlupsmpFTkKHocXne22UsbByAaVQ3t_sG2Jg6LQljtqD3Ao6rjstvYneITjOek-tTfekanBL9chgN1C8gX2LQPr1-7gVGM=k-no""],""When"":""2025-8-23""},{""Name"":""Regina Crichlow"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWANZ1XjN-dXMMJqjOJdJPmoP7Tze8p8s9t_PLSZQ_976YVLNBn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100"",""Rating"":4,""Description"":""I love this restaurant so much! You know a restaurant is doing something right when no matter what you get on the menu it tastes good (in my opinion of course). My favorite meal is the lamb chops. But I’ve also had their vegetable korma, fried fish, and spicy lamb tibs. I’ve enjoyed them all the same. My main gripe is the portion size. While the food tastes amazing, I feel like for the price paid we should get more food. Also the staff could be a little friendlier. I understand when it’s busy you might not greeted with a smile but I’ve come at different times and it’s always the same level of disinterest. Other than those two things, I still think the food is yummy enough to keep coming back."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Luis Ponce"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL9H9d9dsJNeEfUCsxOyMZJR4a_xizfWQ4Df-doMnCCEqwOMA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":3,""Description"":""10/10 taste.\n0/10 old chicken.\nI ordered a butter chicken platter.\nAlso didn’t come with naan. Not sure if it comes with it but if it doesn’t it really should.\nNonetheless, delicious flavors."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Sam H"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKECCGoMLb5oUXka2DyeQspUE2LrNepbrad6pZvBdw6z448hSk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""This is our go to spot whenever I want something flavorful and don’t feel like cooking. Our favorites are the fried chicken wings, butter chicken and goat biryani. Never disappoints, so much flavor!"",""Images"":null,""When"":""""}]",null,
