HAw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""I had a very good experience here! The staff are always so friendly and welcoming. Sometimes I get delivery, and the food always arrives very fast. Other times I call ahead for pickup, and they always have my food ready on time. The staff speak English, Spanish, and even Arabic, which makes communication very easy. I’ve ordered many pizzas here, and every time the service is excellent. They even come outside to put the pizza in my car, which is so helpful. Highly recommended!"",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Henry Coleman"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI9lyXLETDWYheGKCPwpAB0HCQF_erR83pFtHWIhsj7SAZMhw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""I found this pizza spot while running errands and decided to try a slice. It ended up being one of the best decisions of the day. The slice was hot, cheesy, and cooked perfectly. The people working there were warm and inviting. Even though I came in last minute, they served me with a smile. I’m already planning to return this weekend."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""MJ"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKgLLH2-TkT6Xmtso2HvsbYWSY88qJd1CfMCGR4i8PfUQfaRw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100"",""Rating"":3,""Description"":""They donot have pizza by the slice. that was a wrong older review that took me to this place. It is a Dominos type mostly take out place. some seating is available."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1s0l6TxmUW9Upz_9VmKlun-k2mrUp0AknS0n280qlONoEOEtz3XE6XYlETNsgbrBfHVcdIWq3bxWyfes6ZRvUInsRdTdWFRJM5_dyjbzglO4FCp_37a6S9JgOzltCRiWUoNoSIeam-1V2g=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Sfek6dkXf7IIDymzzaltOO9Ym26EvEFxxucpcGVSm3z7w3fxlRcpBF1cZ-rslaG86nJF7i1kSnvYrmXg4f8So0LapZsRViBh3nLcE3vPpec-07il71-PUWetbc_WcBPqP03ILbkPAkpY3=k-no""],""When"":""2026-2-19""},{""Name"":""Sean Tinker"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.