PpSfk9497We182ckb1vs3r5Q0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""It's absolutely worth the wait!\nThai at Laurel has been on our must-try list for a while, and I’m so glad today was the day we finally visited. From the moment we walked in, the staff was warm and welcoming, and the service was impressively fast. The restaurant is spotless and charmingly decorated and cozy yet modern.\n\nNow let’s talk about the food. I rate it 10s across the board!\nWe ordered the Drunken Noodles with chicken, and the flavor was incredible. The Street Noodles were simple yet absolutely perfect. While the dish only came with two shrimp, the taste was so delicious that it honestly didn’t matter.\n\nThe portions are generous. There is plenty to enjoy at the table, share with a friend, and still have some to take home. We’ll definitely be back!\n\nGlobal Sistas Food Review"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn200A8L2pIkDvAdjRw0LGLBGRoc0fX_99VgOFppuzdeXNqwtseG7lyYYkRmo20cs0SH641-piIkUSGtYUEFuMw9jTWzW4quPbwwiqvo4Bizqmoqzcheq7-zD_xJMElb7vs9lab5YQ=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn31QwWFK4tBbF2WrUpfCgpLQUcWTb8TiWkBMW9uAz3g3bw73WIzhFezgzUd8U9XTH-dgazv4lN3-ww1kHJLKSXQd7JKm3QTeap7rVhmvBRpgw02GvXDR7ePbjf2Nx3BtrVaQ8hM=k-no""],""When"":""2025-6-14""},{""Name"":""Huỳnh T. Hiếu - Huynh Liam LLC"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXSn3AF5xKevvRBM1wZtRH3ic6J4ndY-fmO0G-w2fC4WIQcSVk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""The food at Thai at Laurel is very high quality — bold and flavorful. If you enjoy spicy food, this place delivers a solid Thai spice level that really hits the spot 🌶️🍛🔥🇹🇭"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn37_qw4GYcGdrKCp0opnl7shSdp-932e2GFzRoUsiLqKAdeJJ9XITcfZ6TA9SpXa2nhbNNrQSW0XGmJhKXPtIfjx-OF3QtzteUDLU94GsI6EX7b1FN0JEwNYGGY22M4EgIKrS8h1_QoDLfc=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1caZc6pzo4usy8sjoYORbcPOJF81SqynwyhOsu