et side which im not a fan of. But i went out on a limb (after all this was my 1st time here) and ordered a seafood thai red curry and it DID NOT dissappoint! It was was VERY nicely seasoned.....the spice was on point! The portion was a nice size. Im more of an every three hour muncher so I  could only eat half \u0026 took home rest (which heated up just as tastily) Their service was exceptional! They brought out the dessert with a flare candle and a cute little sign! The decor was nice, bathroom clean. It wasn't overly crowded but then the staff was so efficient that they served many tables and customers steadily came and went while we sat there. Overall 👌👌🫶🏽🫶🏽😋 I'd definitely go again and highly recommend!"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn07a20YW6FSQFyu9a4QSDVEJlrHmFUfE0Y4YcdeFRgXt0yH4v1yl5CDpnwdJQntO7A20C1rCAxEmTJc01Mt3-CVlVA5F30ldF_7kGGTGZhOK-Uu3dScIRskM5c7y0jfPK8bIlle=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3B8K542GciSGZo8VuFx6bXkSvawjHKszd7FBTF53mq2GmX4Ui0j_OpRBfHxQw4KTvupnu8tTo-nhmChj3LE6IYnF34ejj7bL3mp8lsl_IYqrIPDuNbFXBKyAOMl6NEfxlXoEXG=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1BxUQ2FMxlV_4wj175ud89gf3x0av5YdCfwfGnFqVMEf4fapjwgnAjN5y2MnL0_UN393fcuVyH_7n6pxvQ8sT2Ut9KnMjsReHiR12OvQukUehmSkEJ2QcXwtFZers_44w6wNQe=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1SxglDn1qN-pUU8vVs7QcLOZKjHBFl8-D_97pm-FDCp__I_0BA3jpxHdSZQsJWzznmBVAz8KhTgZlAYpmUGZYhO4DV9rrkzU_wt87FH9EjTZxvHnOCI0B0V9K63Nxgf4ervIQG=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn09fjKklJTlYJBO4BGR5NKxXKXXOVDOrx_BYAe7iVhSIC2JkTALELRgbgTkBFIXortErYgeKlnq007QhUbdKk86M8WV_i2METVK9bguEx33pBJHO9e0d-E9x8cp0EuctY1oQNnj=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1pNN8HDfPjQkUkAznEA4-cW0dU1MfmeY9rucq3ZPbA6ZwBnOPBJXzNPDET4iosGt2pJAvoYpmtnwJgDglBPjHhRI0Yp3_JhD_mnjr5xAFwglDvOGRFu3tXDKNU8FjcwY8tMHHCuw=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1moYpt1mCW02VEIk-TPXkdLwq7FnZkK_0gKZXYfQ8k81oppyt6-_0aVzC