rder jerk chicken meal for my daughter which she said was delicious and just Jerky(sorry not shown). Great customer service, their online/delivery pick-up stations are really helpful and keeps others from accidentally getting mixed up. Even though the restaurant may not be that big in size it’s still has a openness with small seating area to eat or wait for food. Only thing I can say negative is that there’s a L.A. Fitness next door in the shopping center which take up parking from other stores but I was able to find parking infront. Will definitely be back if we’re back in Laurel area again. Thanks for lunch Negrils and dinner ☺️"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2ZJHunFqTR3eKdH4qwd95_3yMCfomHI8TpD7yKjOVuRFYmQQ90pU3NJoHsqA7y6zQKLnRsEAPn7ReDIt87eru0uZH2Fpqj3QX3fLOLrWBtSAmKy4FyW6V_xkGW-N7SlwBuFcO4nscVbOks=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn09lf_M3l6EBHknNg-dj2zqyLgYafVm4hUQdQsUTOI-Gl7TPMsuchfcVp0OoYAjnuPkVKMMVYzo3c-99md8xHyTYL1mM6jLISDaxpHqMuL_9_SNvZTI39zl1Z4FkyhNaHEFO5NPq-LQVB4=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1IGFNN94yfIlto-WK80sLi5J2XWIoGjxm-Cna45vgZcJ3NUbP75eCXisrlgdjjiUsQVzSBQ4MYrlb4kf4KQYyAqusxejPXi5yxMlbSEXpim42cpEiwMe3GZ90munkHJ53JMzPS7cPbzwOB=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn239fSvYF_1qt7wi5VfAOLIi2TEFBXdAvdj9qf6YxfEfcOy_J1tkUlW4ugdVwZ_jvGVe5KSiGv1OzjhcILkmfmUr2HKxxCSG2UIfjr_-epHYtDgwasnlMNxCQMfqH5mcMe65CpwvrSt7afz=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0g88yxpEUNYJTFCVRrPncwtJWQuKBUYwUDHsc55pAan3Evnu6Nwo6ZIGPjbPsq0NQOUMuHBSpP39sLRYlZ61hlrYaOinlZFujA-_OKT43D_uCxuEEJrGNkwJl9rLU4LGlwlxU7I3g28-DW=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1xbdmKx2hDvCYIHKgEIS7Lj6J0ypjNB-KQRSJEC8SjNkF5158tAozGu39N6DjynbCBMLjuDE3yzm-DZiLLJtAAhanMYEFf8f9orG3nrKQLhoGzPJ2jvFDwdAJnT11ZSTW86S_e2pZ5wEw1=k-no""],""When"":""2026-3-10""},{""Name"":""Daniel Kaisamba"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI6e_1uH42x_I1vA8w-dj2_9HjKB0LVXaq1phE3TA5VXAP8xkY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Negril Jamaican Eatery really surprised me! I ordered oxtails with white rice, cabbage, and one beef patty… but after one bite I ran back and got two more because it was THAT good. The oxtails were so soft they were practically sliding off the bone on their own. I don’t even like lima beans, but somehow they made them taste amazing. And the dumplings? A rare blessing most Jamaican spots don’t bother with. Everything was hitting… honestly, the whole meal had me ready to come back the next day."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3DENTYArY9CltEpn9sVdhdasmszcVsjIN1Mtc2CiH1ncstBDSaXcRFnrQcfakNPKvbjEQ9nGr54Um9U2ZayF8SZB_4jL5pqg5FNHCgOkzv3aerJ12TbT9TRiLg2wsabL__gV0YIeDHu5f3=k-no""],""When"":""2025-11-25""},{""Name"":""QueenBald\u0026Beautiful S"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLjJCydSiNz6XpZ5Z6Mig6NztuW49PXRXZI06dMPjTdnqdASalA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Great seasonings and portion size.\nI would definitely order from here again.\nNOTE: My picture shows AFTER I hate half my rice and cabbage."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Z4p_-_m0sXT1boPQc1nkAWfTSNqEKLF1M6tsHoToK5XZiQi33h2s4xuetSD4ZgyokteYww5sAgn7JsH-yVIT9WYAUE5-vsgyFzs7Za7q6SD2gNi8L5Em4LkDZwZF2IkZXaLLPK3niyOut=k-no""],""When"":""2025-11-24""},{""Name"":""Aaron Rayson"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0Hl1A17E-OX-3gRVmMzJ0cTVMY-pohvy67IAXoe8xir5VUB8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""From the moment I walked in, I felt like I was back home. The vibes were high, the music was nice, and the food? Top notch! The jerk pork was the best I’ve had since leaving Jamaica…perfectly seasoned, tender and full of flavor. Everything tasted authentic like how it is supposed to. The staff were friendly and welcoming and the service was quick. Big respect to the chef - I’ll definitely be back."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0tl509Fky3Gnm8HoObGrumPpGCcc7q0pDt-Lg7MoXpGExNPoVDSDAo7DtbNgQxZsgU5i2mYPGafoNSF0xYFofrwim_bzVSKb-5cpi0sh2yeZHU1fJNsY65HIC6cWKWwLZbbrqP9qCsVEA=k-no""],""When"":""2025-7-22""},{""Name"":""Thaimc"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKtwRMaGaO0iDLJVkLMRUbOSft0PS9zytXVN26eVFpSwkGBzQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":4,""Description"":""I had the curry chicken with rice and veg. It was quite tasty, inexpensive and the portion size was good, but there were a little bones ground up with the chicken so lotsa spitting. Seems this place is mostly focused on takeout and food delivery business. I ordered at the counter, tipped and was expecting to sit and eat but there’s hardly any seating. They called my number, gave me a big to-go bag and charged me for the bag. A bottle of their own branded water was overpriced."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Deserie Johnson"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXP_RqNBgVIn3vjMONsoMbClBQUkj60QjeHLCRygJ4O_NIcxFVyPg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""I haven't eaten at Negril in years because I no longer live near any. When I saw one near my office, I couldn't help but get me some. This Negril in Laurel, MD lived up to my memories. My food was packed well, tasted delicious and filled my belly. I ordered the snapper and all the patties, shrimp, chicken and spinach. The sorrel drink and the sourdough drink were both amazing! I was hungry...no pics."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Dominic"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXps1sjO5G34xU0iLfAi0zE-D9MVzx1zdozlYPXxm7mMnINL35S=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""This place is better than advertised! The Jerk Chicken Sandwich and Beef Patties tastes exactly like my adventures in Jamaica. Highly recommend this place to fellow travelers like myself"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1idG9RxAtpITBZflK3ZEPe6sFeCRuFC-7yo9Gc77RcRSViFC6kewJ-Bpemv-Px7kC_TLPNXms-79vbkR3VUTalMtoaidjUifwPCZlElXXEGCOaeFEFuhRTgDwSCtjZ3xzXRHtkwg=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0E_hA4uhTK_CvzfTD2dd0t7T__G2GHS8QiTX3JYG9wWry4v_llXPEBJFn9wVvUWUO3nMJ-oL_K0LiPT2el0osYceSHIJv8EB3sBH25NSHnd2N2UtH0OTiTL-YtCcE_s1bCgdDx=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2a6X6z8Gbq-oMdf3pIyPBOZK6uMexxvljY3YOTS4GPBp3X6h4N0nBHc-rN4yk_P1wDh0vzet2_Cr9-PHYEIeo1bhv4d-ZerowprgbeWBq4GFteLy7Fwra_6bXOqahFLCxPBfRbOw=k-no""],""When"":""2025-2-28""}]",null,
