ld give the big players some competition. I got the tenders, trout, and mushrooms.  It was sad to say very mediocre.  The tenders were huge, but the batter wasn't seasoned.  Was fried to perfection though.  Trout had better seasoning, but a few surprise bones made it less than enjoyable.  Mushrooms were also just ok.  It is amazing value for the amount of food but needs to amp up the flavor to compete with larger chains.  Staff were helpful, and food came out fast, though not fast food fast.  The store I went to had 2 tables, so it was mainly a place to grab and go."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn08NRFa8ZjiCfZ-WtwyG9Dp9rxVYcZ8iVipGzxaZVOMuRxrUlgsrNUX4okH8KlNB5Uk44hhiXNeud6FanQJr800130JvJbsnpc47T5ct8pS5uKo4LWEoeGNRwfZtzuDByHmADcR=k-no""],""When"":""2024-2-11""},{""Name"":""Eunice O"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJztkyGOOhNTSMmo7S5Fu-H2QJBfE9RJAcMZXzJ5NJnkCbE-g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":3,""Description"":""When this location first opened, everything was great. The management was great. After a poor experience yesterday from when I called the store to place an order. Then coming in to place the order due to poor communication over the phone. I can tell things have changed. After leaving I called because one of the sides had been left out but still poor communication so i called this morning hoping to speak to a new person and i was told nothing can be done about that and that there is no manager to speak to, sorry, and good bye. I am giving 3 stars only because all my prior experiences have been great. Last night the macaroni was old, the fish was dry and they did not put the fries in the pan like they usually do. Then to top it with poor service. I am not sure I would come back especially if the food quality and the service is going to be mediocre to poor."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2HHmAetQ-IA6TjdDPOQAuKTm8zpF68o_2546CDY6qJXyIGT6b3K1QXmHo2BKv2PyoRfjcpuvRzeH