-Pj1Q0PesH751ZK3WMH905jRkIC9iTBFNIoPc9SBcm0Z_swS3kXhxMiM1or8Xka6_7JS8-Eded8lFtejPw-w1dvh8HAv6majpS-Ka-Rpruya24cKiIYiP2P1NpGOTzT-Qdb1F=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0IUUjJM4fQ9mi-fgtsBVptuJY_Mbv5p-po8Hlz9oN5JHqd6JxxprZi4LNzasF7gPtXDlOtGuwtn0CMK7UfGfVDhy0S0mqlGMOJ35fLdJ3icUz5P_iZwc2BzOnMPZI_ch02sHvwd1crziAR=k-no""],""When"":""2025-7-6""},{""Name"":""LOL U SALTY"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbbwWFgWEIYRSkc4GV5kepxghoXOcsGYmp5qNym_a87UGLkKWL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""This location was amazing. Very good food and quality. Ordered delivery from the Checker's app.\n\nAs of January 2026:\n$4 Unbeatable Meal Deal is available here. The best deal ever and the food is too good. This location is amazing. Please don't get rid of this amazing $4 meal deal.\n\n5/5"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3IZzARwb47OCFYKxWAGg82CfzX5PPuU8znMmhEdmaPfESr_Cc11KGO1oCtWYoMQNacqGDMh85wVHluMeZ0iKXNdDpHsbIX3Egnwr-1M1UMuQkkrbHqzfx2mL8y2q-VC_W01oT5Wzj3LNU=k-no""],""When"":""2026-1-13""},{""Name"":""Bunni Rabbit"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQiUmkz7kBLMbY0G1vI-WZenL1LZJOwRIyQwUi8Ah25YSTkxhb=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":1,""Description"":""I would love to actually not give any stars. I ordered a baconzilla meal no mayo, big Buford meal and 5 wings. I was told it was gonna be a wait for the wings and I was cool with that. I was told to pull around to the parking lot and they would bring my food to me. 20 minutes passed and one of the employees came out to my car and told me to pull back around to the drive thru to get my food. I pulled back around and waited. When someone finally came to the window I got a confused look like they didn’t know what I was there for. I told the guy I didn’t receive my food and he said it’s not his fault, what did I get and closed the window. At that point I started to get really angry and I’m sure he could tell. I sat there for another 5 minutes and he came back with the baconzilla meal, wings and some pies, said sorry for the inconvenience and closed the window. I checked the bag and saw that I was missing the big Buford meal. I honked the horn to get the guy attention he ignored me. Another couple of minutes went by he came back again with another sandwich no fries.\n\nWhen I finally got home my boyfriend and I opened our sandwiches and both were drenched in mayo and the baconzilla had no bacon. Please don’t go here after 12am if at all. Complete waste of money and rude staff. I will NEVER go here again."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3cGRSVVeEUwBt2hH_FXtBo3Q2WKdWXXgT4XUiltZUypFLeCFEMR7B9HNLNh--FxXzPCzr7LtdWnzeVNSfYMX3S4fsdxX7F4egG0Gq5hmxhzwh4up-HUBetq0inI-Fb-7TixfdRxA=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1KDMYSVaBDnsVTWT95HyBZXX3jNv-WPyNii8udS_TzBvDpv_v4W_0kjMNJIKoI8SAIPR4C1E_6MSoM4F2LRkhrFl7lTXmdAXWTexzc-aT1B7hz50e76RBgBiFDOh_aogPInOFL=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0AS4C_XAVEPTd54dkG_f9BIIZz7841zJ3Jgu1ifted_sAUTMdTwsWhOm_-XnPQ9BtoP5US34jTjAKBbfcwY3x6j9Ha3DlK2v2fIVvd_33xMaDNytBPhFNFg2kMjcLlQeI3VhRi=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0d_OxIlI7fWB45ujbUza1ydi5DBec4P4xfI9W_6sa8YqmgSR7SYiDelgE11WfBM-_YThCn_kGNgKvBa93j1XI9_-ovh_N9_W6X7rQE7KQCjB0n5A_zm0pFHVyEkMszmkkUX7Hp=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Yzqsc_9kPDAxq-ThuxoOGJasDF1Wq7n926D1wLLhk7Q8zU6Y4RxunL2c5bVPvSDFXk3raKHdwHnzOiSTCbe4YdL8wK2tGmHlicIRR9_1zcJvGamVu3HeAFRrxYHDoNAMHnAVKbw=k-no""],""When"":""2025-4-11""},{""Name"":""Jada Edmonds"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIkf4zEuYFlIrfO4UkU65NFeOqFx9m_UihwqXsvuZF4otoTFA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""As soon as I pulled up to the menu screen I was greeted and helped which was very convenient due to the fact that I was in a pinch for time. She read back my order correctly and had good manners. When she handed me my food she reminded me that I requested pickles and mayo with no tomatoes which I felt was really good skills as a fast food worker! All I have to say is thank you for the speedy accurate and excellent service. I asked for her name because her hard work needed to be recognized. Jade with the lavender hair."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Andrea King"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJ0mlUS9w69YKBm9Tu_bzrWZ3fLotNrPE8XDhV1yTnFwWzCqzC_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":3,""Description"":""Stopped for a quick bite. Wanted their special, which is no longer being offered.  Instead got another special that was posted for $4.99 and got charged $5.99.\nI was told the extra charge was because my order was a \""medium\"" even though I didn't request a medium. I didn't argue. The food was just so-so, but I won't be back anytime soon."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Joshua Williamson"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKl9ys_1XanKc1uxgtz1d5DhSFRpPnzANDOvb29WIs6j2gw3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":1,""Description"":""DO NOT GO TO THIS CHECKERS. Go to any other one but this location. The staff is rude, irritable, aggressive and unprofessional. The person taking my order was literally yelling at me through the speaker because apparently I was taking to long to order, mind you I'm trying to order for 5 people (myself and 4 others in the car with me) and we were the only car there so they weren't even busy. We canceled the order and went to the McDonald's down the street instead. I will not spend my money at a place where they treat you like that. Checkers, you either need to fire the entire staff and bring in new people who are polite and were raised with manners and I don't know...RESPECT or just shut this location down altogether."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Kristianna Sanders"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6B_rjm-56530n3De4tdtM2Sy9JgaYIirWlhPMep9sgbxvQnED=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""I love this checkers down. I think the  manager name there is jade she is so sweet and caring she offered me help I didn't even need just doing her job to make sure the customer was satisfied. she didn't even complain when the elderly lady was taking forever,  just treated her with great mannerism and care. Just never before seen. I had to go on here and brag about the young lady. The franchise needs to know about her immediately. Thanks JADE for making my entire day the food was great."",""Images"":null,""When"":""""},{""Name"":""Andrea Davis"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ6-1bUR5UzfM3umKQAhHv9Q2ovSPir-2zjo6eulkMIaUOsug=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":1,""Description"":""Quality has definitely went down years ago checkers used to be so good and affordable now it’s over priced and you recieve cold food. Best thing u can get here is apple pies or a ice cream without breaking the bank smh"",""Images"":null,""When"":""""}]",null,
