th of food, that'll tell you how good. Huge portions of sides and meats every time I come here. Entrees are so juicy and delicious. The restaurant is always super clean, staff is friendly,  food always fresh and portions are plentiful. Definitely recommend the fried chicken, fried catfish, stuffed salmon, turkey wings to start off with. For sides: mac and cheese, cabbage, collard greens, steamed broccoli, my favorite is the kale mixed greens and the teriyaki string beans are really good. Mom said the ribs were really good too. Every time I go I try something new. Also we tried the $10 rum punch and long Island drinks were good."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn38PqbIOQWZBKY3Rrrpise3uGxUA_sS5Cyrdo2vtp-APUAKugSQkmKkaG_M8Cr1P-uNK3OjSyI-Qd1TLwqzWYqp9nWROqFH8FkFARe68ierWeH4ykaBHqFBJSmql3WTGPHro70ptsYesp1H=k-no""],""When"":""2025-12-14""},{""Name"":""Nashawn Mays"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVb4P4Dss9-9ZvoUXYZzX6K0VrGsl8wssrAYYkspriW8gryF1mh4g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""This catfish dinner is a soulful masterpiece that hits every note of comfort and flavor. The fish is tender and flaky, with a golden crust that’s seasoned to perfection, slightly a bit salty, not too bland, just that ideal balance that makes each bite sing. The sautéed peppers and onions layered on top add a pop of color and a sweet-savory kick that elevates the whole dish.\n\nThe mac and cheese is rich, creamy, and unapologetically indulgent, exactly what you want from a Southern-style side. It’s got that baked-in goodness with a velvety texture that clings to the fork. And the broccoli? Smothered in a smooth cheese sauce that turns a simple veggie into a crave-worthy companion.\n\nPortions are generous, presentation is inviting even in a takeout container, and the lemon wedge tucked under the fish is a thoughtful touch that brightens the plate.\n\nIf you’re looking for a plate that delivers warmth, comfort, and a taste of home, this catfish dinner is it. I will be coming back!!"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2aO5kmDDbnXFourLhNHNIxqFgRNvYQ9_blo3XdneM25SIvXbB4h7xGBmzZkHAtJDB3-VCdltZdqJ2IqDf1lxkG0hwcA40Pufi1h_TSAaZsotgRnJof-yubmx00z_Fo_veIF4Oy6Mz1lkEN=k-no""],""When"":""2025-12-7""},{""Name"":""Donnetta Parker"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLvfL1Y7WztTU6IiKjJLRgv28bwcOX3ZitLO3xZ_otJqx9QkA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""My sister introduce me to this place. I just love the atmosphere, how spacious it is and how clean it is.The staff was nice. l went on a weekend so is was very busy.But most of all l love the fish and noodles with vegetables. Everything was delicious 😋. l love the music they were playing .We were in  there jamming to the music while we were waiting on our food."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3BqwSoYtrCxiOjBDDw_n9RjweCrQMemKobbKTE9lBkHkGOHinn9n1N6XIwim7kIi2xrIYLVZTv7letVT2hSaLkKEul-gZMoyGGfmsnbe9aseQ4kQc72OCgAsRhYbFtuB-1CvlIDUkZ4gJn=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1M15dIJWcOsQ_6hH1q3UZdFErqLv0TB5fyM4klm1UUetwO5X11msofdW4tmmuWuNnNjTlHKaumcTS8nZVxVCNR5XD7KTit5a9LBmnp2CMbN7UNth44cQl7bZ7znuZDz5k0PdmXKa9DEseU=k-no""],""When"":""2026-1-21""},{""Name"":""Elise Wai-Freeman"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvy4L-hMh-MLZz18PISf74yCXINiPacFznAH0beeY07E5krXg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Love love love this place! The food is always good and hot. They have great workers and the restaurant stays clean.\n\nI actually made a review video that’s having great traction!  I’ll attach below check out my page if you want more content like this. (Etoosharp)"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1noZaPmPjNjU2BUsozLGk2AxzxANjcis_mXdLjqedPHsFHn1q2bvlHc3X8Z-wR1l-tfh5iGmqHcqo6OaNsVt_PqIOcPzYzvU12jEUYEk2hF4QBYQ1CeS_qRgTlYJ5NKywz1AjCoPVNQWY=k-no""],""When"