"id"":""children"",""name"":""Children"",""options"":[{""name"":""Good for kids"",""enabled"":true},{""name"":""Good for kids birthday"",""enabled"":true},{""name"":""High chairs"",""enabled"":true},{""name"":""Kids' menu"",""enabled"":true}]},{""id"":""parking"",""name"":""Parking"",""options"":[{""name"":""Free parking lot"",""enabled"":true},{""name"":""Free street parking"",""enabled"":true},{""name"":""Paid parking lot"",""enabled"":true},{""name"":""Parking"",""enabled"":false}]},{""id"":""pets"",""name"":""Pets"",""options"":[{""name"":""Dogs allowed outside"",""enabled"":true}]}]","[{""Name"":""Maira Z"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuVxXIbTFoMNCmzF1YcAjW-2d_20dM9_Iyy-6tOLRCE0qCkxU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""This Mexican restaurant is an absolute gem — hands down the best Mexican food I’ve ever had. It’s our go to place almost every other week. Everything about this place is just amazing, from the food to the vibe. The portions are incredibly generous, and every dish is packed with flavor and made to perfection. Our favorites include carne asada, burritos, fajitas and caramel flan.\n\nThey celebrate birthdays so well, making you feel truly special, so don’t miss this spot if you’re planning a birthday celebration. The energy, the atmosphere, the music — everything comes together to create such a fun and unforgettable experience.\n\nHonestly, the vibe alone is worth coming for, and when you add the outstanding food and warm hospitality, it’s perfection. Five stars from me across the board — food, service, portions, and atmosphere. This place is a must-visit!"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2OKlWnow0ZIMF0afUE74XrmpZZiqCCcSxtH9PLW3MqMeY5ttAnUTbM-oPENnsgY1UKzclVIf_cZxVUu5KAaBmbO4hEepuQnpGheVF8HVIHfA6j2KLsfNqTjtLuocYGijeb8RIeFpk3NlUI=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0PmOtFtlCnwFYA-E2nFwM6YHVuWSU7g_HDUyW7Y25IfbebREDNn4XuNzVRHz1GWzbwWq64XGD4l590