sh —  it seasoned just right and it was delicious.\n\nOne small suggestion: please consider serving lemon on the side rather than squeezing it directly onto the food. While I understand the intent is to enhance flavor, not everyone enjoys lemon, and in our case, the chicharrón had a strong lemon taste that overpowered the dish. If the lemon were served separately, it would allow guests to add it as they prefer — a simple fix for an otherwise flawless meal.\n\nAside from that, I highly recommend Chido’s to anyone looking for delicious Tex-Mex with top-notch customer service. I’ll definitely be coming back!"",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3FPMUPwNxzlrjFXpLT7-cesaXibTyKxsYMOzZfs-DAXQ9SMPQkeCIZYkUnnUQEfIBAyhz3_dnYnkONPuSWTGab85dwo1zsEv5Cv0ZkFuk4vdt2x_97Am_id3IvT2GLnvo_EHKsFUkdjNQ=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3wfGwPNTUFqYl8nGxMD9tuP1i6ItMoihubJLcrf7FURC32_o1i-byxjSTHkieqTquyo7Tp9GalMe51QpxTDDHFBLyeJpZtmOKVSAQoUDoioycgGzRItGteI6w9LLWO1_6paKP47ff9vxc=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1c6Gu7aVbUX9s28Qktg1ONkRwXyp9WSWO3LxSPzBd84adplBoVgbb2ig7DJZuaefXGRhCzXolL0iiw5w_rw1HSsN3uD7hTRs-I6u1Vxa8t_8noYXaOCzrkKUhacfoToqHo-F_ivhe0tizU=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3cwmAw-h1GpwQi2M6sqsLofu0R4kBNprduCCT_zjKQ7hzTt2yYaQZA37W1PByhDSnsbNiyfJlmIQh-97NlwyPEsvY2ojoFui-h9LoUL8ZiwknluL52H5A7yYYYU0UMKnf420aAFa3Pqd2g=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2y1g3zf9IXeoir8dInd74z0mMJLGyWJwHI05b5Dd9m9URL7t9MNynBHjW-nT2cfu4LPaEPkAK1rYokopJdkAfhpalARJ_SOW-SugjnV_fY2ARr_rflUNPbdBoebE61K_nV2jgblCJpDySu=k-no""],""When"":""2025-9-21""},{""Name"":""Renee Abney"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj39lq3umeHi1uxQlGiSd0FnbWO4GGqe8idZqphMnuelaGhznZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""Food was great! Drinks were delicious. Also it’s so cute on the patio section. I really enjoyed my fajitas and it wasn’t too crowded. I really enjoyed this place."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0-yhAwLcW4w7xNvxdXf8W7w---hx7Gpk8qtQKkCApyd07ym1Wj8uialIgxHxETWeA5_yL13XPrehWj3ORkj4Lk-rXJ8NW_E2kdEsQQHdfO5vnIU7jWReIZm_UTaoWOsZUt4IVpzQ98cYmP=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2DTpjy9bwFuFlbUUbynCYC6QAXGDhjVgjlr8M3sBnQtU2KYe6_8eiRQL724bdSYKc7WVTrWQMED2kG1GMQaFDjq6_ZFjklJX9rf6XLZKPbRKihyIwh-6CRRZ-JWSsCuuoUUVh1K3bnb3gv=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1iAnSa8Je3RIR03Qtb7-mVg6WrV5EdyR6iMlFE-lfQXNVGEokP589eBlI1X_Ui1fhXrDatr52Kh94Qcqkc4XQHV2Cxbn__kWfFT_mwM072RqYovtJ8Bf_v18qXiXIK9gXBDDjGlcmUskk=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0rq5vNBaTPuagKXxdEnl4YobhKXlFjvMgjNah-gbT5lNZt-ncVBMi9Id5zNWlB4SCvALb3zrvn4QTdcJ4WMdNFDZZB9MXLv9GSJ7kjqm4laS_iDhCBYAVu0E4hckN29yY8mRt-TDhPmpQ=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3XzGeaAkDjsyj0X3F6lepAK-PwkBucDN4QwzacgB1UGGUiagpoyAl1tCi78zyb_Xd79y67vG36W4zuzgUtNz7pou3mB_BBhj6MHLciyXOSe8RmDk6mAn9nIpGI_22PPCJvuIB162TZN6ph=k-no""],""When"":""2025-12-5""},{""Name"":""cory peterson"",""ProfilePicture"":""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlqggfdoDPHpVwsXIdeoURQdPpX0Nu59Pz09KbXwo9by8ZgLg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100"",""Rating"":5,""Description"":""This spot caught me by surprise — and in a good way. It earns a solid 4 stars from me. The food? Quality is there. Prices? Sure, they’re on the higher side, but no worse than what you’ll find at other Mexican restaurants. In that sense, it’s par for the course.\n\nBut here’s where they separate themselves from the herd: the beer prices are downright insane — in the best way possible. I’m talking 24oz drafts all day, every day, for $6–$8. Let that sink in. Yuengling, 24oz, $6. Modelo, 24oz, $8. That’s the kind of pricing that makes you forget you could’ve dropped the same cash on one cocktail elsewhere, or even on a tomahawk steak at Fleming’s.\n\nI’m fine paying full freight for tacos and fajitas when the drinks don’t feel like I’m mortgaging my house. $14 tacos? Good. $20 fajitas? Solid. Combo plate with three choices at $16? Fair deal. Food is flavorful, portions are right, and nothing felt phoned in.\n\nBottom line: if you’re a beer drinker, this place is worth your time. If you’re just here for the food, you’ll still leave satisfied. But together? It’s a winning combo. We’ll be back — and next time, we’re bringing friends and colleagues along for the ride."",""Images"":[""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3DA-MEHDaAiRDmVnuDqqZyJuOSDRdoLxI3YRhRPzQlVfPUbKfNEuSBSRqanxUhCRUwWXy4loEqaoX0zsiR3Ya-BFuofI6zz8AXa8gUF7FbDQutv3C4ojhdUfj9nAtE982Top7ar8GUKQ8=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn22tvnIocileKDIZNOgb-8t0s9Kg0U5ZtRgod0eOu74LUk6O7KgubnCcVlsqanzTxuU13Nk380fBsojz37IJFq2JZXW2gH9ReXVH4FL3vcMmz1dJVVqurCH0I_3TU8_GjYR-Gkymy0Mt8PT=k-no"",""https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3TXotPy53fD60gFGrxdqmNtxFQ01rE0V1U5loDYiQ9FnMDtFXI2pqRyizFIsDO0ca6Va4MPcxmvYKj5V-CNmMKyq6rdtBlciCoF1N8eFa2AiOWm3fbLBkq7ATGvti0BheE_T-IgxXMv7g=k-no""],""When"":""2025-9-20""}]",null,
